00:03:03.258 --> 00:03:05.193 position:10% line:89% align:start
Good, well, that's a relief.

00:03:05.226 --> 00:03:06.529 position:7% line:89% align:start
We'll be waiting.

00:03:08.029 --> 00:03:09.498 position:33% line:89% align:start
Mm-hmm, yeah.

00:03:11.100 --> 00:03:13.336 position:21% line:89% align:start
Okay. Drive safe.

00:03:16.405 --> 00:03:20.076 position:27% line:83% align:start
Kun, honey,
Mommy's on her way home.

00:03:20.109 --> 00:03:22.111 position:27% line:77% align:start
Yeah? Really?
[woman] She sure is.

00:03:22.144 --> 00:03:23.145 position:61% line:89% align:start
You excited?

00:03:23.179 --> 00:03:25.014 position:30% line:89% align:start
Super excited!

00:03:25.047 --> 00:03:26.916 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hooo! [barking]

00:03:26.950 --> 00:03:28.485 position:5% line:89% align:start
What a cute little puppy.

00:03:28.518 --> 00:03:31.555 position:5% line:83% align:start
You know, babies like
things nice and neat.

00:03:32.289 --> 00:03:34.157 position:13% line:83% align:start
Hey, can the puppy
clean up too?

00:03:34.191 --> 00:03:36.294 position:61% line:5% align:start
'Kay.
Wanna do it on your own?

00:03:36.327 --> 00:03:38.496 position:58% line:5% align:start
Okay.
What a good big brother.

00:03:38.529 --> 00:03:39.597 position:61% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:44.202 position:5% line:83% align:start
Grandma will be
right upstairs.

00:03:44.235 --> 00:03:45.436 position:75% line:89% align:start
Mm-hmm.

00:03:46.504 --> 00:03:49.441 position:21% line:77% align:start
[barking]
[vacuum whirring]

00:03:50.108 --> 00:03:53.178 position:19% line:83% align:start
I don't think I'll ever get
used to these modern homes.

00:03:53.212 --> 00:03:55.414 position:16% line:83% align:start
I guess this is what you
should expect

00:03:55.447 --> 00:03:58.283 position:13% line:5% align:start
when you let your daughter
go off to marry an architect.

00:03:58.317 --> 00:04:00.452 position:5% line:5% align:start
Isn't that right, Yukko?
[barks]

00:04:00.486 --> 00:04:02.888 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whirring]

00:04:09.396 --> 00:04:14.601 position:19% line:83% align:start
Uh... Oh, Kun, you were
supposed to be cleaning up.

00:04:14.634 --> 00:04:16.936 position:5% line:83% align:start
Which do you think
the baby likes more?

00:04:16.970 --> 00:04:19.340 position:5% line:89% align:start
The E233 or the Azusa?

00:04:19.373 --> 00:04:22.410 position:33% line:83% align:start
I don't know, I'm sure
either will be fine.

00:04:23.042 --> 00:04:26.480 position:5% line:77% align:start
Oh, I think Yukko
wants you to play in
the yard with him.

00:04:26.514 --> 00:04:27.314 position:50% line:89% align:start
Really?

00:04:27.348 --> 00:04:28.616 position:5% line:89% align:start
Why don't you go?

00:04:28.649 --> 00:04:30.117 position:50% line:89% align:start
Okay.

00:04:31.753 --> 00:04:33.355 position:5% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:04:34.523 --> 00:04:36.691 position:16% line:83% align:start
Grandma will clean
this up, okay?

00:04:43.398 --> 00:04:45.500 position:41% line:83% align:start
They're gonna
be here any minute!

00:04:45.535 --> 00:04:48.504 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:04:48.538 --> 00:04:49.505 position:5% line:89% align:start
Ready? Fetch!

00:04:49.539 --> 00:04:51.674 position:41% line:77% align:start
[barks]
[ball squeaks]

00:04:53.543 --> 00:04:54.644 position:5% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:04:54.677 --> 00:04:57.046 position:64% line:89% align:start
Go fetch!

00:04:57.079 --> 00:04:59.148 position:5% line:89% align:start
[ball squeaks]

00:05:04.153 --> 00:05:05.322 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:05:06.022 --> 00:05:08.459 position:19% line:89% align:start
[gentle music playing]

00:05:09.660 --> 00:05:13.430 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:05:46.700 --> 00:05:48.235 position:44% line:89% align:start
Cool.

00:05:50.237 --> 00:05:51.571 position:5% line:89% align:start
[car engine rumbling]

00:05:51.605 --> 00:05:52.706 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:05:52.739 --> 00:05:54.608 position:30% line:89% align:start
[barking]

00:05:58.211 --> 00:05:59.279 position:10% line:89% align:start
What is it?

00:05:59.312 --> 00:06:01.248 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Kun grunting]

00:06:06.087 --> 00:06:07.188 position:24% line:89% align:start
Kun.

00:06:07.221 --> 00:06:08.756 position:21% line:89% align:start
[barking]

00:06:11.325 --> 00:06:12.728 position:58% line:89% align:start
Mommy!

00:06:14.596 --> 00:06:17.198 position:10% line:83% align:start
[man] Welcome to your castle,
my little princess.

00:06:17.366 --> 00:06:18.534 position:47% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:06:25.107 --> 00:06:26.275 position:30% line:89% align:start
Hi, we're home, Kun.

00:06:26.308 --> 00:06:29.278 position:33% line:83% align:start
[sobs]
What took you so long?

00:06:29.311 --> 00:06:31.347 position:35% line:89% align:start
I was so lonely here!

00:06:31.381 --> 00:06:33.116 position:5% line:89% align:start
Are you feeling any better?

00:06:33.149 --> 00:06:35.084 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry I was gone
for so long.

00:06:35.485 --> 00:06:38.488 position:33% line:83% align:start
[gasps]
Is that the baby?

00:06:40.256 --> 00:06:42.526 position:19% line:89% align:start
Let me see, I wanna see it.

00:06:48.899 --> 00:06:51.802 position:21% line:89% align:start
[soft music playing]

00:07:00.144 --> 00:07:01.546 position:5% line:89% align:start
This is your baby sister, Kun.

00:07:03.381 --> 00:07:04.849 position:30% line:89% align:start
Sister?

00:07:06.351 --> 00:07:07.820 position:41% line:83% align:start
[mother]
Isn't she precious?

00:07:14.327 --> 00:07:16.562 position:41% line:89% align:start
She is.

00:07:17.563 --> 00:07:19.765 position:27% line:83% align:start
[mother] You have to be
gentle with her.

00:07:27.306 --> 00:07:28.575 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:07:30.277 --> 00:07:31.645 position:5% line:89% align:start
[father] She's awake.

00:07:32.713 --> 00:07:34.281 position:5% line:83% align:start
I think she's staring
at you, Kun.

00:07:34.314 --> 00:07:36.851 position:21% line:83% align:start
[mother] Come on, her eyes
can't even focus yet.

00:07:36.884 --> 00:07:39.654 position:5% line:83% align:start
[father] Well, she sure looks
like she's staring to me.

00:07:40.922 --> 00:07:43.725 position:27% line:83% align:start
[mother] You must always
be nice to her, okay?

00:07:44.759 --> 00:07:45.793 position:44% line:89% align:start
Okay.

00:07:45.827 --> 00:07:48.563 position:16% line:83% align:start
[mother] And you have to
protect her, no matter what.

00:07:49.464 --> 00:07:50.665 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:07:54.402 --> 00:07:55.437 position:21% line:89% align:start
Always.

00:07:55.471 --> 00:07:57.840 position:30% line:89% align:start
[all laughing]

00:07:57.873 --> 00:08:01.877 position:27% line:77% align:start
Oh, hey, Kun. So what do
you think we should name
the new baby?

00:08:01.910 --> 00:08:03.212 position:21% line:89% align:start
I can pick?

00:08:03.880 --> 00:08:08.852 position:16% line:83% align:start
Let me see...
Ah, Nozomi.

00:08:08.885 --> 00:08:10.820 position:35% line:89% align:start
Nozomi, it's not bad.

00:08:10.854 --> 00:08:13.356 position:55% line:83% align:start
Yeah, not bad.
Anything else?

00:08:13.390 --> 00:08:15.258 position:27% line:89% align:start
Or maybe Tsubame.

00:08:15.291 --> 00:08:18.795 position:30% line:89% align:start
Tsubame. Okay, Tsubame.

00:08:20.296 --> 00:08:23.299 position:64% line:71% align:start
Tsubame?
Those are just the names
of his bullet trains.

00:08:23.333 --> 00:08:24.669 position:30% line:89% align:start
[all laughing]

00:08:24.702 --> 00:08:26.537 position:16% line:89% align:start
[father] Of course they are.

00:08:27.304 --> 00:08:29.473 position:5% line:83% align:start
I really wish
I could stay longer

00:08:29.507 --> 00:08:32.878 position:5% line:77% align:start
but I'm afraid your grandma
needs me to help her out
with a few things.

00:08:32.911 --> 00:08:35.513 position:24% line:83% align:start
It's okay, we'll be fine.
Thanks again for coming.

00:08:35.546 --> 00:08:37.481 position:10% line:83% align:start
Call me if you
need anything.

00:08:37.515 --> 00:08:39.216 position:19% line:89% align:start
Thank you so much, Mom.

00:08:39.250 --> 00:08:40.585 position:30% line:89% align:start
Give Dad my love, okay?

00:08:40.619 --> 00:08:43.355 position:5% line:83% align:start
Bye, Kun. Grandma's going
on a bullet train now.

00:08:43.388 --> 00:08:44.623 position:33% line:89% align:start
Bye, Grandma.

00:08:44.656 --> 00:08:46.625 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'll see you soon,
little one.

00:08:46.658 --> 00:08:48.493 position:30% line:89% align:start
Say, "Goodbye, Granny."

00:08:48.527 --> 00:08:50.963 position:21% line:89% align:start
[soft music playing]

00:08:58.371 --> 00:09:00.907 position:33% line:89% align:start
[horn blares]

00:09:08.615 --> 00:09:10.284 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:09:10.317 --> 00:09:11.652 position:19% line:89% align:start
[mother] Good morning, Kun.

00:09:11.685 --> 00:09:13.554 position:5% line:89% align:start
Good morning, Mom.

00:09:15.689 --> 00:09:18.525 position:16% line:89% align:start
Good morning, baby.

00:09:19.761 --> 00:09:21.029 position:21% line:89% align:start
[light music playing]

00:09:21.062 --> 00:09:22.262 position:69% line:89% align:start
[hissing]

00:09:22.296 --> 00:09:23.498 position:52% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:09:24.766 --> 00:09:26.835 position:19% line:77% align:start
[dings]
The toast, right!

00:09:27.969 --> 00:09:29.337 position:27% line:89% align:start
Toast!

00:09:29.671 --> 00:09:32.340 position:44% line:83% align:start
[father cries out]
Okay, I'm ready.

00:09:32.373 --> 00:09:35.845 position:21% line:83% align:start
Breakfast coming right up,
just one minute here.

00:09:35.878 --> 00:09:37.947 position:19% line:77% align:start
I want more milk, Mom!
Milk!

00:09:37.980 --> 00:09:39.982 position:44% line:71% align:start
You got it, buddy.
There you go.
No!

00:09:40.015 --> 00:09:41.517 position:16% line:89% align:start
I want a banana, Mom!

00:09:41.550 --> 00:09:43.285 position:47% line:89% align:start
Okay, banana!

00:09:43.319 --> 00:09:45.454 position:38% line:77% align:start
One banana coming--
No!

00:09:45.488 --> 00:09:46.957 position:19% line:89% align:start
Listen to me, Mom!

00:09:46.990 --> 00:09:47.958 position:52% line:89% align:start
Hey.

00:09:47.991 --> 00:09:49.593 position:27% line:89% align:start
[cries out]

00:09:49.626 --> 00:09:51.928 position:21% line:77% align:start
[vacuum whirring]
[soft music playing]

00:09:58.869 --> 00:10:00.570 position:19% line:83% align:start
Okay, I'm vacuuming
this room now

00:10:00.604 --> 00:10:02.639 position:16% line:83% align:start
so you gotta pick up
your toys, okay?

00:10:05.375 --> 00:10:07.678 position:5% line:89% align:start
Mommy!

00:10:07.712 --> 00:10:09.514 position:44% line:89% align:start
You're all clean.

00:10:09.547 --> 00:10:10.548 position:5% line:89% align:start
[cries out]

00:10:10.581 --> 00:10:11.783 position:58% line:89% align:start
Oh! Yes, Kun?

00:10:11.816 --> 00:10:13.952 position:5% line:89% align:start
[both] Congrats on the baby!

00:10:13.986 --> 00:10:15.553 position:19% line:83% align:start
Yeah,
thank you so much.

00:10:15.586 --> 00:10:16.855 position:5% line:83% align:start
[woman] I bet
she's adorable.

00:10:16.889 --> 00:10:18.624 position:16% line:83% align:start
Well, lucky for her
I think she got

00:10:18.657 --> 00:10:20.025 position:19% line:83% align:start
all her genes
from her mother.

00:10:20.058 --> 00:10:22.461 position:16% line:83% align:start
They say the second one
is supposed to be easier.

00:10:22.494 --> 00:10:25.397 position:7% line:83% align:start
Honestly, it was all such
a blur, I don't really remember

00:10:25.430 --> 00:10:26.965 position:5% line:89% align:start
what it was like with Kun.

00:10:28.067 --> 00:10:29.903 position:47% line:83% align:start
I heard that Yumi
was planning on

00:10:29.936 --> 00:10:31.871 position:44% line:83% align:start
going back to work
right away.

00:10:31.905 --> 00:10:33.940 position:21% line:83% align:start
That's right, because
one of her colleagues

00:10:33.973 --> 00:10:36.009 position:16% line:83% align:start
is about to have a baby,
can you believe it?

00:10:36.042 --> 00:10:37.977 position:5% line:83% align:start
She told us you'd be
taking care of the house

00:10:38.011 --> 00:10:39.879 position:5% line:83% align:start
and looking after the kids,
is that right?

00:10:39.913 --> 00:10:42.016 position:13% line:83% align:start
Yeah, no, it's just 'cause
I decided to go freelance

00:10:42.049 --> 00:10:43.783 position:21% line:83% align:start
so I'll be working
from home from now on

00:10:43.817 --> 00:10:45.585 position:13% line:83% align:start
which means I'll have time
to take breaks

00:10:45.618 --> 00:10:47.922 position:21% line:83% align:start
and tidy up around
the house and stuff.

00:10:47.955 --> 00:10:49.690 position:10% line:77% align:start
Must be nice.
That's impressive.

00:10:49.723 --> 00:10:52.059 position:33% line:77% align:start
It's nothing.
I wish my husband did that.

00:10:52.092 --> 00:10:53.594 position:24% line:89% align:start
Stop, it's nothing.

00:10:53.627 --> 00:10:56.330 position:50% line:89% align:start
[father humming]

00:11:01.435 --> 00:11:03.605 position:61% line:77% align:start
Hmm, what?
Nothing.

00:11:03.638 --> 00:11:05.574 position:41% line:83% align:start
You can tell me.
Come on, what's up?

00:11:05.607 --> 00:11:07.776 position:5% line:77% align:start
All right, if you insist.
Mm-hmm.

00:11:07.809 --> 00:11:09.611 position:5% line:83% align:start
You just can't help
yourself, can you?

00:11:09.644 --> 00:11:11.413 position:5% line:83% align:start
Doing your
"I'm the perfect husband" act

00:11:11.446 --> 00:11:13.015 position:5% line:83% align:start
in front of all
the other moms.

00:11:13.049 --> 00:11:16.652 position:55% line:71% align:start
What?
You do realize they can
all see right through it.

00:11:16.686 --> 00:11:21.023 position:66% line:77% align:start
[sizzling]
[crying out]

00:11:23.659 --> 00:11:25.628 position:5% line:89% align:start
That cloth is for the table.

00:11:26.629 --> 00:11:27.831 position:69% line:89% align:start
No!

00:11:29.833 --> 00:11:32.936 position:7% line:77% align:start
Look, March is just
around the corner
and I'll be back at work soon,

00:11:32.970 --> 00:11:35.672 position:16% line:77% align:start
which means you'll have
to actually start
taking care of the house

00:11:35.706 --> 00:11:37.808 position:16% line:83% align:start
instead of just bragging
to others about it.

00:11:39.543 --> 00:11:40.677 position:41% line:89% align:start
I know.

00:11:40.711 --> 00:11:42.546 position:5% line:83% align:start
I can't do everything
by myself

00:11:42.579 --> 00:11:44.581 position:5% line:83% align:start
like I did
when Kun was born.

00:11:45.449 --> 00:11:46.551 position:41% line:89% align:start
I know.

00:11:46.584 --> 00:11:47.986 position:21% line:89% align:start
[soft music playing]

00:11:48.019 --> 00:11:49.988 position:33% line:83% align:start
I'm your big brother,
so I'm gonna teach you

00:11:50.021 --> 00:11:51.856 position:33% line:83% align:start
a lot of
different stuff, okay?

00:11:53.658 --> 00:11:55.127 position:16% line:89% align:start
First, I'll take you outside

00:11:55.160 --> 00:11:57.662 position:21% line:83% align:start
and I'm gonna teach you
the names of all the bugs.

00:11:57.695 --> 00:11:58.731 position:47% line:89% align:start
Dragonfly!

00:11:59.965 --> 00:12:02.101 position:10% line:83% align:start
Then I'll show you how you
can see things in the clouds.

00:12:02.134 --> 00:12:04.136 position:16% line:89% align:start
There's a scorpion! See?

00:12:05.104 --> 00:12:08.208 position:10% line:71% align:start
And that one--
[Yumi] She's too little
to go outside just yet.

00:12:08.241 --> 00:12:10.709 position:5% line:83% align:start
You can take her when
she's a bit bigger, all right?

00:12:10.743 --> 00:12:12.112 position:35% line:89% align:start
Fine.

00:12:23.991 --> 00:12:26.093 position:10% line:89% align:start
"The Witch and Mr. Mustache."

00:12:26.127 --> 00:12:28.729 position:19% line:83% align:start
The witch was woken up
by Mr. Mustache,

00:12:28.763 --> 00:12:30.731 position:30% line:83% align:start
so she got mad
and chased him.

00:12:31.799 --> 00:12:33.601 position:21% line:89% align:start
And Mr. Mustache ran.

00:12:33.634 --> 00:12:36.971 position:10% line:83% align:start
He got away by jumping onto
a train on the Yamanote line.

00:12:37.004 --> 00:12:39.174 position:13% line:83% align:start
Then the witch tried to
follow him by jumping onto

00:12:39.207 --> 00:12:41.843 position:24% line:83% align:start
a different train
on the Keihin line,

00:12:41.877 --> 00:12:44.012 position:30% line:83% align:start
but the two trains went
different directions

00:12:44.046 --> 00:12:46.882 position:30% line:83% align:start
at Tabata station
and they got separated.

00:12:46.915 --> 00:12:49.218 position:24% line:89% align:start
Knock... it... off!

00:12:50.052 --> 00:12:53.222 position:5% line:83% align:start
It's her nap time,
you need to let her sleep.

00:12:53.256 --> 00:12:54.756 position:33% line:89% align:start
[crying out]

00:12:54.790 --> 00:12:56.092 position:19% line:89% align:start
A bit more.

00:12:56.125 --> 00:12:57.093 position:47% line:89% align:start
You sure?

00:12:57.126 --> 00:12:58.661 position:16% line:5% align:start
Push it in more.

00:12:58.695 --> 00:13:00.163 position:21% line:5% align:start
I don't want her to choke.
Hey, Mom!

00:13:00.196 --> 00:13:02.098 position:5% line:5% align:start
If you don't, she'll suck in
too much air, then--

00:13:02.131 --> 00:13:04.867 position:58% line:5% align:start
Hey, Dad!
Listen to me!

00:13:04.901 --> 00:13:06.769 position:38% line:5% align:start
Oh, wow, she's
really going for it.

00:13:06.803 --> 00:13:08.805 position:19% line:5% align:start
Right, now lift her up.
Hey, Mom!

00:13:08.838 --> 00:13:10.808 position:30% line:5% align:start
I don't think
I'm doing this right.
[Kun] Stop ignoring me!

00:13:10.841 --> 00:13:12.810 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] Don't be so
nervous, it's just gas.

00:13:21.152 --> 00:13:23.520 position:19% line:83% align:start
Okay, so this detergent,
this one is for the whites.

00:13:23.554 --> 00:13:25.924 position:33% line:71% align:start
[father] Not colors.
[Yumi] Right,
just whites.

00:13:25.957 --> 00:13:27.524 position:38% line:83% align:start
[father] Wait,
what if it has both?

00:13:27.558 --> 00:13:29.961 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] Well, it's not,
it's not an exact science.

00:13:30.762 --> 00:13:32.230 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:13:51.851 --> 00:13:55.889 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Kun panting]

00:14:06.800 --> 00:14:08.770 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckling]

00:14:21.749 --> 00:14:23.551 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]

00:14:25.087 --> 00:14:26.355 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Yumi]
Kun, what happened?

00:14:26.388 --> 00:14:28.257 position:44% line:83% align:start
Why is she crying?
What did you do?

00:14:28.290 --> 00:14:30.059 position:35% line:83% align:start
You promised that you
would be nice to her.

00:14:30.092 --> 00:14:31.660 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's not my fault, okay?

00:14:31.693 --> 00:14:33.862 position:24% line:83% align:start
Look, you have to be
extra gentle with a baby.

00:14:33.896 --> 00:14:35.764 position:13% line:77% align:start
What if I can't?
Just try.

00:14:35.798 --> 00:14:37.267 position:19% line:77% align:start
I don't wanna.
Enough.

00:14:37.300 --> 00:14:40.003 position:30% line:89% align:start
I won't do it!

00:14:42.639 --> 00:14:43.339 position:52% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:14:47.311 --> 00:14:49.779 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]

00:14:49.813 --> 00:14:51.048 position:5% line:89% align:start
[thuds]

00:14:51.082 --> 00:14:52.283 position:33% line:83% align:start
What's wrong with you?
She's a baby!

00:14:52.316 --> 00:14:53.851 position:41% line:83% align:start
You could have
seriously hurt her!

00:14:53.884 --> 00:14:57.788 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]

00:15:02.927 --> 00:15:05.964 position:33% line:77% align:start
[howling]
[kids crying]

00:15:09.968 --> 00:15:12.104 position:21% line:89% align:start
Do something! Hurry!

00:15:12.904 --> 00:15:14.840 position:24% line:83% align:start
Kun, stop it!
You're a big brother now.

00:15:14.873 --> 00:15:16.741 position:41% line:83% align:start
I don't wanna be
her brother!

00:15:16.775 --> 00:15:17.909 position:30% line:83% align:start
Well, you don't
have a choice.

00:15:17.943 --> 00:15:19.644 position:47% line:83% align:start
And you're not
my mom either!

00:15:19.678 --> 00:15:21.180 position:21% line:83% align:start
Oh, yeah? Then who
am I supposed to be?

00:15:21.214 --> 00:15:25.418 position:35% line:83% align:start
You're a witch,
an old ugly witch.

00:15:25.452 --> 00:15:28.121 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm a what?

00:15:31.225 --> 00:15:32.392 position:52% line:89% align:start
Daddy!

00:15:33.360 --> 00:15:34.962 position:38% line:89% align:start
Uh, yeah!

00:15:37.464 --> 00:15:40.267 position:13% line:83% align:start
Everything's gonna be fine,
we're gonna be all right.

00:15:40.934 --> 00:15:42.803 position:35% line:83% align:start
Come on, everything's
gonna be fine.

00:15:42.836 --> 00:15:45.106 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]

00:15:52.714 --> 00:15:54.115 position:5% line:89% align:start
Good job, baby!

00:15:58.287 --> 00:15:59.654 position:10% line:89% align:start
[thuds]

00:16:01.257 --> 00:16:05.961 position:5% line:71% align:start
[sobbing]
[man chuckles]
Life is hard, huh?

00:16:07.963 --> 00:16:10.833 position:21% line:89% align:start
[soft music playing]

00:16:10.866 --> 00:16:12.868 position:55% line:89% align:start
[man chuckles]

00:16:15.405 --> 00:16:19.708 position:7% line:83% align:start
Don't worry, I know exactly
what you're feeling right now.

00:16:19.743 --> 00:16:21.945 position:13% line:89% align:start
Jealousy, plain and simple.

00:16:22.746 --> 00:16:24.080 position:52% line:89% align:start
[Kun] Jealousy?

00:16:24.515 --> 00:16:26.116 position:61% line:89% align:start
What's that?

00:16:27.285 --> 00:16:30.321 position:5% line:83% align:start
Up 'til now, you had all your
parents' love and affection

00:16:30.354 --> 00:16:34.091 position:5% line:83% align:start
all to yourself, but then that
baby showed up from nowhere

00:16:34.125 --> 00:16:36.194 position:5% line:83% align:start
and your world
was turned upside down

00:16:36.227 --> 00:16:38.396 position:5% line:83% align:start
when all that affection
they had for you

00:16:38.430 --> 00:16:40.264 position:5% line:89% align:start
suddenly disappeared.

00:16:40.299 --> 00:16:44.269 position:5% line:83% align:start
You knew you'd get in trouble
if you did anything, but still,

00:16:44.303 --> 00:16:48.207 position:5% line:83% align:start
you couldn't help yourself
so you raised your hand and...

00:16:48.774 --> 00:16:51.443 position:16% line:83% align:start
[chuckles]
Did I get it right?

00:16:52.878 --> 00:16:54.046 position:47% line:89% align:start
Who are you?

00:16:54.079 --> 00:16:55.948 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm the prince,
can't you tell?

00:16:55.981 --> 00:16:56.982 position:47% line:89% align:start
[Kun] The prince?

00:16:57.015 --> 00:16:59.185 position:7% line:89% align:start
Yeah, of this house.

00:16:59.452 --> 00:17:02.422 position:5% line:83% align:start
I've been here since
before you were born.

00:17:02.455 --> 00:17:03.456 position:64% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:17:03.489 --> 00:17:07.060 position:5% line:83% align:start
Now, you must kneel before me
because I'm royalty.

00:17:10.797 --> 00:17:13.866 position:5% line:83% align:start
You know, long ago,
Mom and Dad used to shower me

00:17:13.900 --> 00:17:16.036 position:5% line:83% align:start
with love
and dote on me as well.

00:17:16.070 --> 00:17:18.138 position:5% line:89% align:start
I had all of their attention.

00:17:18.172 --> 00:17:20.975 position:5% line:83% align:start
They constantly told me
what a good boy I was

00:17:21.008 --> 00:17:23.210 position:5% line:83% align:start
and would stroke
my head lovingly.

00:17:23.978 --> 00:17:27.249 position:24% line:77% align:start
Then all that changed!
Ever since the day you
showed up on the doorstep

00:17:27.282 --> 00:17:29.050 position:33% line:83% align:start
they've stopped paying
attention to me.

00:17:29.084 --> 00:17:30.485 position:50% line:83% align:start
Suddenly, all of
my organic meals

00:17:30.518 --> 00:17:32.287 position:19% line:83% align:start
were changed to
the regular generic brands,

00:17:32.320 --> 00:17:34.189 position:27% line:83% align:start
not to mention
the reduction in snacks,

00:17:34.222 --> 00:17:35.924 position:47% line:83% align:start
and they stopped
complimenting me,

00:17:35.957 --> 00:17:39.060 position:13% line:83% align:start
they'd only ever scold me
or just completely ignore me.

00:17:39.094 --> 00:17:41.497 position:5% line:83% align:start
But then I realized
what was going on.

00:17:42.431 --> 00:17:46.135 position:5% line:83% align:start
Their love was being
taken from me.

00:17:46.369 --> 00:17:49.272 position:5% line:83% align:start
[sighs] It made me feel
so empty inside

00:17:49.305 --> 00:17:51.374 position:5% line:83% align:start
like a wolf rejected
from its pack.

00:17:51.408 --> 00:17:53.075 position:5% line:83% align:start
Do you know what
that feels like?

00:17:53.109 --> 00:17:54.211 position:55% line:89% align:start
No, I don't.

00:17:54.244 --> 00:17:56.879 position:5% line:83% align:start
What?
Are you sure about that?

00:17:57.381 --> 00:18:00.250 position:21% line:83% align:start
All right, fine then,
you be that way.

00:18:00.284 --> 00:18:03.387 position:5% line:77% align:start
You can play all innocent,
but this is partially
your fault.

00:18:03.420 --> 00:18:05.822 position:5% line:83% align:start
One day, this is going
to happen to you

00:18:05.856 --> 00:18:07.525 position:5% line:83% align:start
and we'll see
how you like it!

00:18:11.362 --> 00:18:12.397 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:18:13.064 --> 00:18:14.332 position:38% line:89% align:start
[squeaks]

00:18:14.599 --> 00:18:15.933 position:41% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:18:15.967 --> 00:18:17.235 position:55% line:89% align:start
Fetch!

00:18:21.039 --> 00:18:22.308 position:27% line:89% align:start
Here you go.

00:18:23.007 --> 00:18:24.142 position:38% line:89% align:start
Here.

00:18:26.111 --> 00:18:27.179 position:41% line:89% align:start
Fetch!

00:18:27.212 --> 00:18:29.248 position:5% line:89% align:start
[rapid footsteps]

00:18:30.649 --> 00:18:32.151 position:35% line:89% align:start
[man] Here.

00:18:35.455 --> 00:18:36.523 position:52% line:89% align:start
Fetch!

00:18:36.556 --> 00:18:38.090 position:24% line:89% align:start
I got it, I got it!

00:18:38.558 --> 00:18:39.992 position:55% line:89% align:start
I knew it!

00:18:40.025 --> 00:18:42.395 position:19% line:71% align:start
[rips]
[crying out]
What'd you do that for?

00:18:42.429 --> 00:18:43.430 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:18:43.463 --> 00:18:44.564 position:35% line:89% align:start
No, don't!

00:18:44.597 --> 00:18:46.132 position:33% line:89% align:start
[crying out]

00:18:48.134 --> 00:18:50.571 position:16% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music playing]

00:18:57.211 --> 00:18:58.479 position:41% line:89% align:start
[barks]

00:19:03.050 --> 00:19:04.251 position:33% line:89% align:start
Give it back!

00:19:04.285 --> 00:19:05.520 position:21% line:89% align:start
Give me back my tail!

00:19:05.554 --> 00:19:08.055 position:19% line:77% align:start
[Kun laughing]
[soft music playing]

00:19:12.661 --> 00:19:14.096 position:72% line:89% align:start
Stop!

00:19:15.297 --> 00:19:18.066 position:13% line:89% align:start
Aw, man, I'm gonna get ya!

00:19:19.602 --> 00:19:20.436 position:16% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:19:20.470 --> 00:19:23.106 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hey, wait! Come back here!

00:19:23.139 --> 00:19:24.474 position:58% line:89% align:start
Stop running!

00:19:25.942 --> 00:19:27.610 position:5% line:89% align:start
Give it back, right now!

00:19:27.643 --> 00:19:29.412 position:5% line:89% align:start
You can't catch me!

00:19:33.584 --> 00:19:35.285 position:35% line:89% align:start
[straining]

00:19:35.319 --> 00:19:37.588 position:10% line:89% align:start
No, wait! What are you doing?

00:19:38.155 --> 00:19:40.357 position:50% line:83% align:start
What's going on?
You okay?

00:19:41.158 --> 00:19:42.426 position:69% line:89% align:start
Yukko!

00:19:42.459 --> 00:19:45.062 position:38% line:83% align:start
Hey, hey, stop that!
What are you doing?

00:19:45.095 --> 00:19:46.296 position:66% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:19:46.330 --> 00:19:49.367 position:21% line:83% align:start
Yukko?
What is with the dog?

00:19:50.968 --> 00:19:52.637 position:19% line:89% align:start
Look at me, I'm a dog!

00:19:53.605 --> 00:19:55.940 position:16% line:83% align:start
What does that kid
think he's doing?

00:19:55.974 --> 00:19:58.143 position:24% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:20:02.681 --> 00:20:06.385 position:21% line:89% align:start
[light music playing]

00:20:11.657 --> 00:20:12.458 position:19% line:89% align:start
Ruff ruff!

00:20:12.491 --> 00:20:14.427 position:5% line:83% align:start
Hey, I see you've
finally calmed down,

00:20:14.460 --> 00:20:16.962 position:5% line:77% align:start
you're not acting
like a baby anymore.
That's good.

00:20:16.996 --> 00:20:19.666 position:30% line:77% align:start
I don't know what
that was all about,
but I'm glad it's over.

00:20:19.699 --> 00:20:23.003 position:5% line:83% align:start
I wasn't acting like
a baby, I was being Yukko.

00:20:23.036 --> 00:20:25.505 position:10% line:83% align:start
[father] Oh, so does that mean
you can talk to Yukko?

00:20:25.539 --> 00:20:29.242 position:5% line:83% align:start
Yeah, he says he doesn't like
the cheap dog food you get,

00:20:29.276 --> 00:20:30.977 position:5% line:89% align:start
the old stuff was better.

00:20:31.011 --> 00:20:32.680 position:19% line:89% align:start
[father] Oh, is that right?

00:20:32.713 --> 00:20:35.416 position:33% line:77% align:start
Well, I better go out
and get the good stuff
right now then.

00:20:37.051 --> 00:20:38.252 position:55% line:89% align:start
[barks]

00:20:38.286 --> 00:20:41.155 position:21% line:89% align:start
[soft music playing]

00:21:05.815 --> 00:21:07.350 position:50% line:89% align:start
That is so good.

00:21:08.618 --> 00:21:11.187 position:5% line:77% align:start
You know,
I don't know if I'm ready
to do all this on my own.

00:21:11.221 --> 00:21:12.690 position:35% line:83% align:start
What, you mean
like giving her milk?

00:21:12.723 --> 00:21:15.058 position:5% line:77% align:start
Well, whenever
I try to hold her,
she won't stop crying,

00:21:15.091 --> 00:21:18.429 position:5% line:83% align:start
no matter what, but then you
take her and she just stops.

00:21:18.462 --> 00:21:20.631 position:41% line:71% align:start
[Yumi] I'm not sure
what you expected.
What?

00:21:20.664 --> 00:21:22.800 position:24% line:83% align:start
I mean, you didn't
help out at all with Kun.

00:21:22.833 --> 00:21:25.569 position:5% line:83% align:start
Oh, right. I guess I should
have made more of an effort.

00:21:25.603 --> 00:21:28.305 position:38% line:77% align:start
[Yumi] You did fawn
all over me though,
for what it's worth.

00:21:28.339 --> 00:21:30.274 position:13% line:83% align:start
Well, at least I did
something right.

00:21:30.307 --> 00:21:34.179 position:24% line:77% align:start
Oh, I just figured it was
because men aren't
interested in babies.

00:21:34.212 --> 00:21:36.581 position:5% line:77% align:start
[father]
Of course I'm interested,
I was just working.

00:21:36.615 --> 00:21:38.517 position:24% line:83% align:start
What?
You're kidding me, right?

00:21:38.550 --> 00:21:42.487 position:5% line:83% align:start
I swear to you, this guy
is pumped, I am so excited,

00:21:42.522 --> 00:21:44.557 position:5% line:83% align:start
I can't think of anything
more exciting!

00:21:44.590 --> 00:21:46.425 position:5% line:83% align:start
Changing diapers
is gonna rock, yeah!

00:21:46.459 --> 00:21:48.661 position:50% line:83% align:start
Okay, now I know
you're lying.

00:21:50.630 --> 00:21:51.430 position:50% line:89% align:start
Huh? What is it?

00:21:51.464 --> 00:21:54.133 position:5% line:83% align:start
Right, I wanted to
show you something.

00:21:54.500 --> 00:21:55.602 position:27% line:89% align:start
[phone buzzes]

00:21:55.636 --> 00:21:56.570 position:72% line:89% align:start
Okay.

00:21:57.871 --> 00:21:59.038 position:21% line:89% align:start
Well?

00:21:59.973 --> 00:22:02.776 position:66% line:71% align:start
It's nice.
It's meant to be
like a beacon.

00:22:03.243 --> 00:22:04.645 position:47% line:89% align:start
I really like it.

00:22:06.680 --> 00:22:09.483 position:27% line:89% align:start
[birds chirping]

00:22:18.426 --> 00:22:19.794 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Yumi] Good morning, sweetie.

00:22:20.695 --> 00:22:24.299 position:30% line:71% align:start
Morning.
Hey. Turn around,
look behind you.

00:22:25.801 --> 00:22:27.235 position:33% line:89% align:start
What does it say?

00:22:27.268 --> 00:22:28.571 position:30% line:89% align:start
[father] Mirai.

00:22:28.604 --> 00:22:29.471 position:47% line:89% align:start
Mirai?

00:22:29.505 --> 00:22:32.308 position:27% line:83% align:start
It's your sister's name,
it means "future."

00:22:37.714 --> 00:22:39.481 position:35% line:89% align:start
That's her?

00:22:45.154 --> 00:22:46.423 position:33% line:89% align:start
Hello, Mirai.

00:22:48.391 --> 00:22:49.826 position:21% line:89% align:start
That's a funny name.

00:22:56.199 --> 00:22:57.435 position:47% line:89% align:start
Here it is.

00:22:57.902 --> 00:22:59.169 position:50% line:89% align:start
What is that?

00:22:59.202 --> 00:23:01.505 position:5% line:83% align:start
Girls' Day,
to celebrate girls.

00:23:01.539 --> 00:23:02.907 position:52% line:89% align:start
But what for?

00:23:02.940 --> 00:23:04.408 position:10% line:89% align:start
To pray that our little girl

00:23:04.442 --> 00:23:06.477 position:19% line:83% align:start
has a future of health
and happiness.

00:23:06.510 --> 00:23:08.614 position:52% line:77% align:start
[gasps]
Oh, no, you don't.

00:23:09.948 --> 00:23:11.850 position:13% line:83% align:start
These dolls are for Mirai,
you can't touch them.

00:23:11.883 --> 00:23:14.286 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Kun] But I wanna play
with them!

00:23:14.319 --> 00:23:16.388 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Yumi]
Doll's Day is for girls.

00:23:16.421 --> 00:23:19.826 position:5% line:77% align:start
Whoa, you too, Yukko.
No dolls for you either,
you're a boy.

00:23:20.827 --> 00:23:22.729 position:27% line:89% align:start
[doorbell rings]

00:23:23.328 --> 00:23:24.831 position:38% line:77% align:start
Hi.
Welcome.

00:23:24.864 --> 00:23:26.566 position:21% line:89% align:start
It sure is warm here.

00:23:26.599 --> 00:23:29.502 position:24% line:83% align:start
[grandma] Look how
adorable she is!

00:23:29.535 --> 00:23:31.204 position:27% line:83% align:start
One of the perks
of having a girl

00:23:31.237 --> 00:23:34.207 position:13% line:83% align:start
is you get to dress them up
in such cute outfits.

00:23:34.607 --> 00:23:36.844 position:30% line:83% align:start
Can't believe it's been
three months already.

00:23:36.877 --> 00:23:39.546 position:16% line:83% align:start
She weighs twice as much
as when she was born.

00:23:39.580 --> 00:23:41.180 position:5% line:89% align:start
Can she lift her head yet?

00:23:41.214 --> 00:23:42.349 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yeah, just about.

00:23:42.383 --> 00:23:44.752 position:52% line:83% align:start
Mirai, dear,
look over here.

00:23:45.552 --> 00:23:47.688 position:27% line:89% align:start
Smile! [chuckles]

00:23:47.721 --> 00:23:48.756 position:38% line:89% align:start
[babbles]

00:23:48.923 --> 00:23:50.324 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:23:50.357 --> 00:23:51.693 position:19% line:83% align:start
[grandpa]
Kun, you're in the way!

00:23:51.726 --> 00:23:54.361 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm taking a video
for Great-Granny.

00:23:54.395 --> 00:23:56.464 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh, Mirai! Over here!

00:23:56.498 --> 00:23:58.500 position:24% line:83% align:start
Take a video of me,
film me!

00:23:58.533 --> 00:24:01.269 position:21% line:83% align:start
[grandpa] Okay, okay.
Hold on, here we go.

00:24:01.937 --> 00:24:05.473 position:21% line:83% align:start
Oh, that's good.
Yes, yes, very nice.

00:24:05.507 --> 00:24:08.376 position:16% line:77% align:start
Mirai, sweetie!
Wait, I wasn't done yet!

00:24:08.410 --> 00:24:10.780 position:10% line:89% align:start
[grandpa] Sorry, my mistake.

00:24:10.813 --> 00:24:12.715 position:30% line:89% align:start
Oh, very good.

00:24:13.449 --> 00:24:15.451 position:35% line:89% align:start
Mirai! Oh!

00:24:15.918 --> 00:24:17.253 position:21% line:89% align:start
What's that?

00:24:17.286 --> 00:24:18.454 position:10% line:89% align:start
You see this bruise?

00:24:18.487 --> 00:24:19.655 position:5% line:89% align:start
Where is it?

00:24:20.791 --> 00:24:22.626 position:19% line:77% align:start
[grandpa] Here.
[grandma] You're right.

00:24:22.659 --> 00:24:24.594 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] Don't worry,
it's just a birth mark.

00:24:24.628 --> 00:24:26.530 position:5% line:83% align:start
[grandma] Is that
what the doctor said?

00:24:26.563 --> 00:24:29.366 position:13% line:77% align:start
[Yumi] Yeah, he said
it might go away with time
but no guarantees.

00:24:29.399 --> 00:24:32.937 position:5% line:77% align:start
[grandma] I see.
Well, I hope it fades
for her sake.

00:24:34.271 --> 00:24:35.640 position:5% line:89% align:start
[grandpa groans]

00:24:39.844 --> 00:24:42.980 position:10% line:83% align:start
[grandma] The doll emperor
and doll empress are married,

00:24:43.014 --> 00:24:45.783 position:24% line:83% align:start
like Mom and Dad,
Granny and Grandpa,

00:24:45.817 --> 00:24:48.519 position:13% line:83% align:start
and Great-Granny,
and Great-Grandpa, you see?

00:24:48.553 --> 00:24:51.824 position:16% line:77% align:start
[Yumi] You went to
Great-Grandpa's funeral
last year, remember, Kun?

00:24:52.390 --> 00:24:53.425 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mm-hmm.

00:24:53.459 --> 00:24:54.793 position:19% line:89% align:start
Everything looks delicious.

00:24:54.827 --> 00:24:56.628 position:5% line:83% align:start
That reminds me,
is that old story about

00:24:56.662 --> 00:24:58.263 position:5% line:83% align:start
Grandpa and Grandma
really true?

00:24:58.297 --> 00:24:59.398 position:61% line:89% align:start
Which story?

00:24:59.431 --> 00:25:00.799 position:5% line:83% align:start
When Grandpa proposed,
Grandma said

00:25:00.834 --> 00:25:02.769 position:5% line:83% align:start
she would marry him
under one condition.

00:25:02.802 --> 00:25:04.470 position:5% line:83% align:start
She told him that
she would say yes,

00:25:04.503 --> 00:25:07.741 position:5% line:83% align:start
but only if he could run faster
than her, so they competed

00:25:07.774 --> 00:25:10.376 position:5% line:83% align:start
and Grandpa ended up winning
the race and her heart too.

00:25:10.410 --> 00:25:13.446 position:21% line:83% align:start
I have no clue. I've never
heard that story before.

00:25:13.480 --> 00:25:14.814 position:5% line:89% align:start
What?

00:25:14.848 --> 00:25:17.051 position:5% line:83% align:start
But Uncle Yamato told me
that story at the funeral.

00:25:17.084 --> 00:25:19.352 position:33% line:83% align:start
I really doubt there's
any truth to that,

00:25:19.385 --> 00:25:20.420 position:44% line:89% align:start
Dad had a bad leg.

00:25:20.453 --> 00:25:22.389 position:5% line:89% align:start
What, so he just lied?

00:25:22.423 --> 00:25:23.958 position:10% line:77% align:start
[grandma]
I don't know about that,
it was probably just a rumor.

00:25:23.991 --> 00:25:25.993 position:19% line:83% align:start
[grandpa] Oh, hey,
speaking of tall tales,

00:25:26.026 --> 00:25:28.395 position:19% line:83% align:start
what's the superstition
about the dolls again?

00:25:28.429 --> 00:25:30.564 position:10% line:83% align:start
[grandma] It's that if
they're not put away in time,

00:25:30.598 --> 00:25:32.466 position:10% line:89% align:start
her marriage will be delayed.

00:25:32.500 --> 00:25:34.836 position:19% line:77% align:start
[Yumi] Oh, come on,
no one believes
in that stuff nowadays.

00:25:34.870 --> 00:25:37.439 position:27% line:83% align:start
But how late are
we talking here?

00:25:37.472 --> 00:25:40.075 position:13% line:83% align:start
[grandma] One year for
each day they're left out.

00:25:40.108 --> 00:25:44.379 position:16% line:77% align:start
[Yumi] Oh, please.
How do they even come up
with this stuff?

00:25:44.412 --> 00:25:47.650 position:7% line:83% align:start
[grandma] It's superstition.
Who knows where it comes from.

00:25:50.486 --> 00:25:51.821 position:41% line:89% align:start
Oh, no.

00:25:52.588 --> 00:25:54.690 position:16% line:89% align:start
Oh, I'm gonna be so late.

00:25:57.860 --> 00:25:59.729 position:33% line:83% align:start
Okay, Kun,
Mommy has to go away

00:25:59.762 --> 00:26:01.597 position:5% line:83% align:start
for a few days
on a business trip.

00:26:01.631 --> 00:26:02.431 position:38% line:89% align:start
Don't go!

00:26:03.000 --> 00:26:04.935 position:5% line:83% align:start
You better be good
while I'm gone, okay?

00:26:04.968 --> 00:26:05.869 position:30% line:89% align:start
No!

00:26:05.903 --> 00:26:07.004 position:5% line:83% align:start
And don't
forget to tell Daddy

00:26:07.037 --> 00:26:08.872 position:5% line:83% align:start
when you need to go
to the bathroom.

00:26:08.906 --> 00:26:09.706 position:50% line:89% align:start
Mommy, no!

00:26:09.740 --> 00:26:11.675 position:5% line:83% align:start
All right, the kids
are in your hands.

00:26:11.708 --> 00:26:13.744 position:16% line:77% align:start
[Kun] Mommy!
Don't worry, I got this.

00:26:13.777 --> 00:26:15.479 position:16% line:77% align:start
Okay.
Mommy!

00:26:15.512 --> 00:26:16.714 position:30% line:89% align:start
I don't want you to go!

00:26:16.748 --> 00:26:18.016 position:16% line:83% align:start
Don't forget to
put the dolls away today.

00:26:18.049 --> 00:26:20.485 position:58% line:77% align:start
[father] Yup.
Bye, see you in a few days.

00:26:20.518 --> 00:26:21.986 position:24% line:89% align:start
Mom!

00:26:23.054 --> 00:26:25.890 position:21% line:89% align:start
[soft music playing]

00:26:31.462 --> 00:26:35.134 position:16% line:71% align:start
I want Mommy!
I don't want you to take me!
Come on, let's go.

00:26:35.167 --> 00:26:36.735 position:21% line:89% align:start
I know, I know.

00:26:36.769 --> 00:26:38.470 position:35% line:83% align:start
Excuse me,
is this the drop off?

00:26:38.504 --> 00:26:39.939 position:44% line:89% align:start
[crying]

00:26:41.908 --> 00:26:42.943 position:64% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:26:44.778 --> 00:26:47.814 position:16% line:89% align:start
Is this machine washable?

00:26:48.014 --> 00:26:51.084 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whirring]

00:26:53.086 --> 00:26:54.088 position:44% line:89% align:start
Whoa!

00:26:54.921 --> 00:26:56.389 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]

00:26:56.423 --> 00:26:58.926 position:16% line:83% align:start
Oh, no, what's she doing?
What's happening?

00:26:59.093 --> 00:27:00.661 position:24% line:89% align:start
Uh, it's that late?

00:27:06.033 --> 00:27:08.569 position:38% line:89% align:start
[sobbing]

00:27:10.105 --> 00:27:11.505 position:35% line:89% align:start
Why isn't Mommy here?

00:27:11.539 --> 00:27:12.707 position:38% line:83% align:start
Okay,
let's just get home.

00:27:12.740 --> 00:27:14.943 position:19% line:89% align:start
Let's take a nap, okay?

00:27:20.716 --> 00:27:21.984 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:27:27.757 --> 00:27:29.125 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:27:32.161 --> 00:27:34.063 position:38% line:89% align:start
[snoring]

00:27:42.472 --> 00:27:43.641 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:27:51.815 --> 00:27:53.450 position:19% line:89% align:start
Daddy, you wanna play?

00:27:53.484 --> 00:27:54.986 position:13% line:83% align:start
[father] Hmm?
Why don't you go next door

00:27:55.020 --> 00:27:56.453 position:7% line:89% align:start
and see if the kids wanna play?

00:27:56.487 --> 00:27:58.089 position:13% line:89% align:start
But I wanna play with you.

00:27:58.123 --> 00:28:00.625 position:13% line:83% align:start
[father] I thought
you'd rather be with Mommy?

00:28:01.192 --> 00:28:04.029 position:24% line:83% align:start
I changed my mind.
Let's play.

00:28:04.062 --> 00:28:05.664 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hmm. Yeah.

00:28:06.765 --> 00:28:09.068 position:16% line:77% align:start
Yeah, that sounds good.
[Kun] Let's read a book.

00:28:11.636 --> 00:28:13.973 position:5% line:83% align:start
No, wait!
Let's watch a video!

00:28:15.241 --> 00:28:17.176 position:5% line:89% align:start
Or we can play with tops.

00:28:17.209 --> 00:28:18.210 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:28:23.649 --> 00:28:25.185 position:19% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:28:28.188 --> 00:28:32.459 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Kun] Mirai, have you ever
seen a whale?

00:28:34.795 --> 00:28:37.899 position:16% line:83% align:start
I don't like you, Mirai.
You're boring.

00:28:38.532 --> 00:28:40.667 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crunching]

00:28:51.579 --> 00:28:53.048 position:38% line:89% align:start
[moaning]

00:28:56.719 --> 00:28:58.754 position:30% line:89% align:start
[humming]

00:29:02.825 --> 00:29:05.061 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckling]

00:29:05.095 --> 00:29:08.064 position:16% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music playing]

00:29:14.938 --> 00:29:17.107 position:19% line:89% align:start
Again? What's going on?

00:29:26.150 --> 00:29:27.218 position:41% line:89% align:start
[snaps]

00:29:32.957 --> 00:29:34.226 position:33% line:89% align:start
What's this?

00:29:34.859 --> 00:29:36.028 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:29:39.831 --> 00:29:41.733 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's a whale cookie!

00:29:42.367 --> 00:29:43.935 position:5% line:89% align:start
There's another one!

00:29:44.603 --> 00:29:45.837 position:16% line:89% align:start
And here too!

00:29:45.871 --> 00:29:47.873 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:29:59.852 --> 00:30:01.155 position:33% line:89% align:start
Big Brother!

00:30:03.257 --> 00:30:05.825 position:21% line:83% align:start
Stop putting cookies
on my face already!

00:30:06.994 --> 00:30:08.662 position:33% line:89% align:start
Who are you?

00:30:08.695 --> 00:30:11.265 position:10% line:83% align:start
And will you stop hitting me
and trying to make me cry?

00:30:11.298 --> 00:30:12.434 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:30:12.467 --> 00:30:15.803 position:5% line:83% align:start
But let's move past that,
we have more important problems.

00:30:15.836 --> 00:30:17.105 position:61% line:89% align:start
That!

00:30:17.138 --> 00:30:22.811 position:21% line:83% align:start
[gasps] Are you Mirai
from the future?

00:30:23.311 --> 00:30:24.746 position:21% line:89% align:start
[gasps] Stop staring!

00:30:24.779 --> 00:30:26.047 position:35% line:89% align:start
[exclaims]

00:30:30.051 --> 00:30:32.121 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Mirai] A year for each day.

00:30:32.154 --> 00:30:34.990 position:16% line:83% align:start
Now, a year may not seem
like a very long time,

00:30:35.024 --> 00:30:36.325 position:21% line:83% align:start
but what do you think
will happen

00:30:36.358 --> 00:30:38.794 position:19% line:83% align:start
when all of those years
keep on adding up?

00:30:38.828 --> 00:30:40.663 position:33% line:89% align:start
I don't know, tell me.

00:30:40.696 --> 00:30:43.966 position:10% line:83% align:start
I might not be able to marry
the man I love, that's what.

00:30:43.999 --> 00:30:45.835 position:61% line:77% align:start
Oh.
Stop that!

00:30:45.868 --> 00:30:47.337 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Kun] Who are you
in love with?

00:30:47.370 --> 00:30:50.006 position:13% line:83% align:start
Well, nobody yet,
I just meant in the future.

00:30:50.040 --> 00:30:51.842 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Kun] Are you guys
gonna race?

00:30:52.242 --> 00:30:53.977 position:13% line:89% align:start
What are you talking about?

00:30:54.010 --> 00:30:55.645 position:10% line:83% align:start
How should I know?
Just go tell Dad to hurry up

00:30:55.679 --> 00:30:57.348 position:7% line:89% align:start
and put away the dolls already.

00:30:59.683 --> 00:31:00.851 position:72% line:89% align:start
No.

00:31:01.685 --> 00:31:02.786 position:38% line:89% align:start
Why not?

00:31:02.819 --> 00:31:04.688 position:50% line:83% align:start
Because I don't
like you, Mirai.

00:31:04.721 --> 00:31:05.923 position:24% line:89% align:start
Why don't you like me?

00:31:05.957 --> 00:31:07.859 position:50% line:83% align:start
Because we don't
get along.

00:31:07.892 --> 00:31:11.162 position:7% line:83% align:start
Well, you have to help me
because I can't let Dad see me.

00:31:11.195 --> 00:31:12.264 position:66% line:89% align:start
Why not?

00:31:12.297 --> 00:31:14.199 position:10% line:83% align:start
Please! You have to help me,
you're my big brother.

00:31:14.233 --> 00:31:17.236 position:30% line:83% align:start
But I never agreed to
be Mirai's big brother.

00:31:20.005 --> 00:31:23.942 position:7% line:83% align:start
Fine, I get it
and I won't force you to, 'kay?

00:31:24.376 --> 00:31:28.013 position:10% line:83% align:start
But if you won't help me,
then you leave me no choice.

00:31:28.046 --> 00:31:29.882 position:5% line:89% align:start
We'll have to play the bee game.

00:31:29.915 --> 00:31:31.317 position:52% line:89% align:start
[Kun] Bee game?

00:31:34.320 --> 00:31:37.223 position:24% line:83% align:start
You gotta shake
your little bottom.

00:31:37.257 --> 00:31:38.324 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:31:38.358 --> 00:31:41.295 position:24% line:83% align:start
And then you wiggle
when you walk.

00:31:44.465 --> 00:31:49.270 position:13% line:77% align:start
Sting, sting, sting, sting!
[laughing]

00:31:51.739 --> 00:31:53.874 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:31:54.108 --> 00:31:56.378 position:13% line:89% align:start
Well, will you help me now?

00:31:56.877 --> 00:32:00.781 position:13% line:89% align:start
Yeah. Can we play it again?

00:32:00.814 --> 00:32:03.985 position:30% line:89% align:start
[animal sounds]

00:32:05.921 --> 00:32:07.389 position:61% line:89% align:start
Please?

00:32:08.323 --> 00:32:09.425 position:58% line:89% align:start
[Kun] Dad.

00:32:09.891 --> 00:32:10.959 position:38% line:89% align:start
Yeah?

00:32:10.992 --> 00:32:13.162 position:55% line:83% align:start
The dolls
are still out.

00:32:13.196 --> 00:32:14.230 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:32:14.964 --> 00:32:16.999 position:27% line:89% align:start
Should we put them away?

00:32:17.033 --> 00:32:18.267 position:35% line:89% align:start
Mm-hmm.

00:32:19.202 --> 00:32:20.303 position:78% line:89% align:start
Dad.

00:32:20.903 --> 00:32:22.138 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yeah?

00:32:23.773 --> 00:32:25.342 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Mirai] Shoot, know what?

00:32:25.375 --> 00:32:27.910 position:19% line:83% align:start
You're just gonna have
to put them away.

00:32:27.944 --> 00:32:29.779 position:50% line:77% align:start
Okay.
[Mirai] Really?

00:32:29.812 --> 00:32:31.348 position:13% line:89% align:start
No! Hey! Wait a second.

00:32:33.150 --> 00:32:35.252 position:44% line:71% align:start
What?
[Mirai] Show me
your hands first.

00:32:35.285 --> 00:32:36.153 position:41% line:89% align:start
These?

00:32:36.186 --> 00:32:37.888 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Mirai] They're so dirty!

00:32:37.921 --> 00:32:40.291 position:7% line:83% align:start
You know what? Never mind,
I'll figure something else out.

00:32:40.325 --> 00:32:41.226 position:38% line:89% align:start
How come?

00:32:41.259 --> 00:32:43.261 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Mirai nervously]
I'd rather you not do it.

00:32:43.294 --> 00:32:45.296 position:44% line:77% align:start
But why?
[Mirai] Stop doing that!

00:32:46.798 --> 00:32:48.333 position:27% line:89% align:start
I have no choice.

00:33:02.948 --> 00:33:04.049 position:50% line:89% align:start
Oh, no, the box!

00:33:04.083 --> 00:33:05.485 position:33% line:89% align:start
Where is it?

00:33:14.527 --> 00:33:15.962 position:50% line:89% align:start
Found it.

00:33:20.834 --> 00:33:22.102 position:52% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:33:33.014 --> 00:33:34.215 position:55% line:77% align:start
Huh?
[gasps]

00:33:40.855 --> 00:33:42.924 position:38% line:89% align:start
[wincing]

00:33:46.995 --> 00:33:49.231 position:19% line:89% align:start
Oh, my God! She's gone!

00:33:49.264 --> 00:33:52.234 position:30% line:83% align:start
Where's Mirai?
Mirai! Mirai!

00:33:52.268 --> 00:33:53.569 position:21% line:89% align:start
Where are you, baby?

00:33:54.404 --> 00:33:55.271 position:33% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:33:56.139 --> 00:33:59.075 position:21% line:83% align:start
There you are!
You just slipped off.

00:34:00.009 --> 00:34:01.477 position:24% line:89% align:start
[exhales in relief]

00:34:02.211 --> 00:34:04.347 position:5% line:89% align:start
Come on, up you go.

00:34:06.283 --> 00:34:08.218 position:5% line:89% align:start
[man] Did you just see that?

00:34:08.252 --> 00:34:10.354 position:5% line:83% align:start
The baby suddenly
vanished into thin air

00:34:10.387 --> 00:34:12.623 position:5% line:83% align:start
and then mysteriously
reappeared again.

00:34:12.656 --> 00:34:15.059 position:5% line:83% align:start
I wonder why something
like that would happen?

00:34:15.092 --> 00:34:19.129 position:5% line:83% align:start
Maybe it means that the Mirai
from the future and Baby Mirai

00:34:19.163 --> 00:34:21.566 position:5% line:83% align:start
can't exist at the same time
and in the same place.

00:34:21.599 --> 00:34:24.902 position:7% line:83% align:start
Wait a second. If you wanna
question mysterious existences,

00:34:24.935 --> 00:34:26.538 position:21% line:83% align:start
why don't you take
a look in the mirror?

00:34:26.571 --> 00:34:28.606 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm not the one who's a dog
who looks like a human.

00:34:28.640 --> 00:34:30.909 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Yukko] Well, I think
it's normal.

00:34:30.942 --> 00:34:32.043 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:34:32.444 --> 00:34:34.312 position:27% line:83% align:start
We're wasting
our time arguing.

00:34:34.913 --> 00:34:37.015 position:13% line:83% align:start
We have to figure out a way
to get those dolls

00:34:37.048 --> 00:34:38.484 position:21% line:89% align:start
back into their box,

00:34:38.517 --> 00:34:40.219 position:10% line:83% align:start
and we're gonna have to work
together to pull it off.

00:34:40.619 --> 00:34:42.888 position:16% line:71% align:start
Huh?
That means you'll
have to help too.

00:34:42.922 --> 00:34:44.223 position:10% line:89% align:start
Oh, right.

00:34:44.256 --> 00:34:46.292 position:19% line:83% align:start
Big Brother,
your job's to distract Dad.

00:34:47.461 --> 00:34:48.395 position:64% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:34:49.363 --> 00:34:51.198 position:35% line:89% align:start
[nervously chuckling]

00:34:51.231 --> 00:34:52.499 position:5% line:89% align:start
What is it?

00:34:52.532 --> 00:34:56.370 position:41% line:83% align:start
Before that, can we
play the bee game?

00:34:56.403 --> 00:34:57.404 position:16% line:89% align:start
Again?

00:34:58.505 --> 00:35:02.075 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Kun laughing]

00:35:03.478 --> 00:35:04.579 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:35:06.381 --> 00:35:08.882 position:21% line:83% align:start
Waiter, I'll have
whatever he's having.

