Well, at least I tried.

00:40:10.038 --> 00:40:11.506 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Yumi] I'm home.

00:40:11.540 --> 00:40:13.275 position:7% line:89% align:start
[father and Kun] Welcome back.

00:40:13.775 --> 00:40:18.815 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm so tired. There, there,
I'll feed you real soon, okay?

00:40:19.682 --> 00:40:22.284 position:13% line:83% align:start
Oh, thanks for remembering
to put those dolls away.

00:40:22.518 --> 00:40:26.589 position:7% line:89% align:start
