00:40:41.505 --> 00:40:42.539 position:35% line:89% align:start
Wait, what?

00:40:42.573 --> 00:40:44.441 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Kun] And Yukko helped too.

00:40:46.010 --> 00:40:50.280 position:10% line:83% align:start
Oh, yeah! I never told you,
I met Mirai from the future.

00:40:50.615 --> 00:40:52.851 position:10% line:83% align:start
[father]
Oh, what'd the two of you do?

00:40:53.485 --> 00:40:55.286 position:19% line:89% align:start
We played the bee game.

00:40:55.320 --> 00:40:56.688 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh, you did?

00:40:56.721 --> 00:40:58.323 position:19% line:83% align:start
After that, we played
red light, green light.

00:40:58.356 --> 00:41:00.358 position:5% line:83% align:start
Oh, really?
You sure are lucky.

00:41:00.391 --> 00:41:03.863 position:5% line:77% align:start
It must have been pretty
great to have met Mirai
all grown up, huh?

00:41:04.764 --> 00:41:06.632 position:5% line:89% align:start
What do you think, Mom?

00:41:06.665 --> 00:41:07.933 position:58% line:89% align:start
I don't know.

00:41:08.834 --> 00:41:12.338 position:24% line:83% align:start
I don't know. Actually,
I think I'm okay waiting.

00:41:12.371 --> 00:41:15.374 position:35% line:83% align:start
That way, I can watch
Baby Mirai grow up.

00:41:15.876 --> 00:41:19.445 position:16% line:83% align:start
Yeah, me too. I think
I like Baby Mirai better.

00:41:19.479 --> 00:41:21.348 position:30% line:89% align:start
[all laughing]

00:41:21.882 --> 00:41:24.885 position:5% line:89% align:start
[lighthearted music playing]

00:41:34.762 --> 00:41:36.597 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Yumi] Who do you think that is?

00:41:36.631 --> 00:41:38.432 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Kun] Um, it's Mom!

00:41:38.466 --> 00:41:40.334 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] Mm-hmm.
That's right. [chuckles]

00:41:40.368 --> 00:41:41.736 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Kun] Where am I?

00:41:41.769 --> 00:41:43.939 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] You're right there,
there in my tummy.

00:41:44.572 --> 00:41:46.008 position:7% line:89% align:start
[Kun] What kind of baby was I?

00:41:46.041 --> 00:41:48.610 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] Hmm, you were
pretty much like Mirai is now.

00:41:48.644 --> 00:41:50.445 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Kun] But I don't like Mirai.

00:41:50.479 --> 00:41:53.549 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] Oh, you don't mean that.
Don't say that.

00:41:54.650 --> 00:41:56.119 position:10% line:89% align:start
Now who do you think this is?

00:41:56.152 --> 00:41:58.021 position:24% line:71% align:start
[Kun gasps]
It's you, isn't it?
[Yumi] Mm-hmm.

00:41:58.054 --> 00:42:00.589 position:19% line:77% align:start
[Kun] You're so pretty.
[Yumi] Oh, thank you.

00:42:00.623 --> 00:42:01.758 position:30% line:5% align:start
You were skinnier then.

00:42:01.791 --> 00:42:03.526 position:21% line:5% align:start
Hey, watch it, buddy.

00:42:04.460 --> 00:42:05.929 position:10% line:5% align:start
There's more photos in here.

00:42:07.730 --> 00:42:09.966 position:24% line:83% align:start
This one was when
I first met Daddy.

00:42:10.533 --> 00:42:12.669 position:7% line:89% align:start
And this was from my first job.

00:42:13.070 --> 00:42:16.540 position:13% line:83% align:start
That's college graduation,
high school.

00:42:16.907 --> 00:42:20.811 position:10% line:83% align:start
Middle school.
Oh, it makes me feel so old.

00:42:20.845 --> 00:42:23.814 position:19% line:83% align:start
Elementary school,
I had so much fun then.

00:42:23.848 --> 00:42:27.418 position:16% line:83% align:start
First grade.
Oh, look, that's Yoichi.

00:42:27.451 --> 00:42:29.520 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Kun] Yoichi? Who's Yoichi?

00:42:29.553 --> 00:42:31.990 position:16% line:77% align:start
[Yumi] He's Mommy's
little brother. We went
to his wedding, remember?

00:42:32.023 --> 00:42:33.859 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Kun] Did you guys get along?

00:42:33.892 --> 00:42:35.794 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] Yeah, of course we did.
We're only a year apart

00:42:35.827 --> 00:42:37.896 position:19% line:83% align:start
so we were practically
like twins.

00:42:38.430 --> 00:42:39.664 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Kun] You had a cat?

00:42:39.698 --> 00:42:41.600 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] It's not real,
it's just a toy.

00:42:41.633 --> 00:42:43.870 position:16% line:83% align:start
It was a birthday present
from Great-Granny.

00:42:44.637 --> 00:42:46.472 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh, I wanna get a present!

00:42:46.505 --> 00:42:47.640 position:30% line:89% align:start
Huh? What for?

00:42:47.673 --> 00:42:49.842 position:33% line:89% align:start
Um... for my birthday?

00:42:49.876 --> 00:42:51.978 position:19% line:83% align:start
