00:42:57.751 --> 00:42:58.952 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:42:59.786 --> 00:43:03.056 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh, seriously, man.

00:43:04.925 --> 00:43:07.461 position:19% line:83% align:start
