00:43:17.906 --> 00:43:19.607 position:21% line:89% align:start
I can't do it without him.

00:43:19.641 --> 00:43:22.543 position:5% line:77% align:start
Well, fine!
Then I'm just gonna
have to throw them all away.

00:43:22.577 --> 00:43:23.878 position:30% line:89% align:start
You can't do that!

00:43:23.913 --> 00:43:25.948 position:5% line:83% align:start
And I'm never gonna buy you
another new toy again.

00:43:25.981 --> 00:43:28.449 position:33% line:89% align:start
No, Mom! Please don't!

00:43:28.483 --> 00:43:29.752 position:5% line:89% align:start
Then pick up your toys.

00:43:29.785 --> 00:43:33.122 position:47% line:83% align:start
I don't wanna!
[crying]

00:43:35.557 --> 00:43:37.893 position:13% line:89% align:start
Why is it always like this?

00:43:37.928 --> 00:43:39.029 position:33% line:89% align:start
This is Mirai's fault!

00:43:39.062 --> 00:43:40.897 position:19% line:77% align:start
[gasps]
I hate her!

00:43:40.931 --> 00:43:42.766 position:5% line:83% align:start
What, no! What are you doing?
You can't hit her, she's a baby!

00:43:42.799 --> 00:43:44.734 position:27% line:89% align:start
[doorbell rings]

00:43:44.768 --> 00:43:47.070 position:5% line:77% align:start
Great, now Grandma's here.
[Yukko barking]

00:43:57.014 --> 00:43:59.183 position:47% line:83% align:start
Mommy will be
right back, okay?

00:44:00.217 --> 00:44:02.853 position:24% line:77% align:start
[doorbell ringing]
Yeah, I'm coming!

00:44:02.887 --> 00:44:04.755 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'll be right there!

00:44:07.658 --> 00:44:09.027 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yells]

00:44:28.047 --> 00:44:31.084 position:10% line:89% align:start
She's a witch! Mom's a witch!

00:44:31.551 --> 00:44:33.953 position:7% line:89% align:start
