00:44:36.789 --> 00:44:38.524 position:33% line:77% align:start
[door slams]
[groans]

00:44:38.558 --> 00:44:40.761 position:35% line:89% align:start
[bubbling]

00:44:40.794 --> 00:44:43.697 position:21% line:89% align:start
[soft music playing]

00:45:00.081 --> 00:45:01.716 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:45:15.965 --> 00:45:18.168 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Mirai] You really
should be nicer to her.

00:45:19.735 --> 00:45:21.238 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Kun] Future Mirai.

00:45:21.271 --> 00:45:22.638 position:27% line:89% align:start
You did it again.

00:45:22.671 --> 00:45:24.107 position:19% line:83% align:start
