00:45:32.116 --> 00:45:34.285 position:7% line:89% align:start
I don't care what kind it was!

00:45:35.353 --> 00:45:38.723 position:5% line:83% align:start
And why can't you be
a little nicer to Mom?

00:45:38.756 --> 00:45:40.191 position:52% line:83% align:start
