Adorable!

00:46:14.661 --> 00:46:15.962 position:33% line:89% align:start
[crying]

00:46:15.995 --> 00:46:17.364 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hang on, wait!

00:46:17.398 --> 00:46:18.999 position:35% line:89% align:start
Come back!

00:46:20.968 --> 00:46:22.803 position:61% line:89% align:start
Big Brother!

00:46:25.206 --> 00:46:27.275 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]

00:46:54.704 --> 00:46:56.038 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:46:59.476 --> 00:47:01.044 position:35% line:89% align:start
Where am I?

00:47:07.784 --> 00:47:09.987 position:5% line:77% align:start
[girl crying]
Huh?

00:47:32.811 --> 00:47:34.446 position:30% line:89% align:start
What are you sad about?

00:47:39.151 --> 00:47:42.155 position:5% line:89% align:start
