00:47:50.430 --> 00:47:51.798 position:33% line:89% align:start
Thanks a lot.

00:47:51.831 --> 00:47:53.300 position:24% line:89% align:start
You're really nice.

00:47:54.768 --> 00:47:58.139 position:19% line:83% align:start
But to tell the truth,
I wasn't really crying.

00:47:59.207 --> 00:48:01.776 position:13% line:83% align:start
I just wanted to make sure
I was feeling sad enough

00:48:01.809 --> 00:48:02.977 position:21% line:89% align:start
to write this letter.

00:48:03.010 --> 00:48:04.412 position:38% line:89% align:start
[giggles]

00:48:06.314 --> 00:48:07.248 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:48:33.042 --> 00:48:34.410 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Kun] What's the letter for?

00:48:34.444 --> 00:48:36.980 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] Dearest Grandma,
I really would like

00:48:37.013 --> 00:48:39.048 position:47% line:83% align:start
to have a cat
so please let me.

00:48:39.082 --> 00:48:40.484 position:61% line:89% align:start
[Kun] A cat?

00:48:40.517 --> 00:48:43.220 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] I don't know why,
but animals love me.

00:48:43.254 --> 00:48:45.923 position:10% line:89% align:start
Every animal I meet loves me.

00:48:45.956 --> 00:48:50.060 position:5% line:83% align:start
But my grandma, she's allergic
so she said I couldn't have one.

00:48:50.094 --> 00:48:52.464 position:5% line:83% align:start
She said I could have
an outdoor pet,

00:48:52.497 --> 00:48:55.567 position:5% line:83% align:start
but it's not a real pet
if it's always outside,

00:48:55.600 --> 00:48:58.403 position:5% line:83% align:start
so I'm going to write her
a letter every single day

00:48:58.436 --> 00:48:59.504 position:5% line:89% align:start
until she says yes.

00:48:59.537 --> 00:49:03.241 position:5% line:83% align:start
I can be pretty convincing,
so I think she'll let me.

00:49:04.976 --> 00:49:07.112 position:35% line:89% align:start
[growling]

00:49:07.380 --> 00:49:12.585 position:21% line:83% align:start
Here kitty, come on.
No need to be scared.

00:49:12.618 --> 00:49:14.086 position:19% line:89% align:start
I wanna be your friend.

00:49:14.120 --> 00:49:16.188 position:33% line:77% align:start
[cat snarls]
[gasps]

00:49:26.066 --> 00:49:27.968 position:21% line:5% align:start
Do you have any
brothers or sisters?

00:49:28.001 --> 00:49:29.202 position:61% line:5% align:start
[Kun] Yeah.
[Yumi] Which?

00:49:29.236 --> 00:49:30.504 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Kun] A little sister.

00:49:30.537 --> 00:49:33.307 position:30% line:83% align:start
I have a little brother
but he's so weak

00:49:33.340 --> 00:49:37.278 position:10% line:83% align:start
and such a crybaby,
always crying over everything

00:49:37.312 --> 00:49:40.914 position:7% line:83% align:start
and 'cause of that my mom
loves me more than my brother.

00:49:40.948 --> 00:49:44.252 position:5% line:83% align:start
Even if my grandma says no,
I have a feeling that my mom

00:49:44.285 --> 00:49:46.421 position:5% line:83% align:start
will eventually
let me have a cat.

00:49:49.023 --> 00:49:50.292 position:5% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:49:50.326 --> 00:49:53.295 position:5% line:83% align:start
I guess I should be glad
my brother's a crybaby.

00:49:55.431 --> 00:49:56.432 position:27% line:89% align:start
We're here.

00:50:13.283 --> 00:50:15.185 position:33% line:89% align:start
[clattering]

00:50:15.586 --> 00:50:19.055 position:35% line:77% align:start
Oh, you can play with
my brother's toys
if you want.

00:50:23.427 --> 00:50:25.329 position:16% line:83% align:start
Won't you get in trouble
for doing that?

00:50:25.563 --> 00:50:28.866 position:30% line:83% align:start
Probably, but it's
funner when it's messy.

00:50:30.201 --> 00:50:32.303 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:50:34.606 --> 00:50:36.006 position:33% line:89% align:start
You're right!

00:50:36.040 --> 00:50:37.476 position:5% line:89% align:start
Are you hungry?

00:50:46.118 --> 00:50:47.353 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:50:49.555 --> 00:50:51.290 position:5% line:83% align:start
Help yourself
to anything you want.

00:50:51.324 --> 00:50:53.493 position:52% line:83% align:start
[Kun] You might
get scolded.

00:50:54.527 --> 00:50:58.097 position:13% line:83% align:start
Probably, but it tastes
better when it's messy.

00:51:11.245 --> 00:51:12.647 position:33% line:89% align:start
It's so good.

00:51:12.680 --> 00:51:13.981 position:30% line:89% align:start
I know, right?

00:51:14.014 --> 00:51:14.948 position:72% line:89% align:start
So good!

00:51:14.982 --> 00:51:15.717 position:5% line:89% align:start
So good!

00:51:15.750 --> 00:51:17.217 position:30% line:89% align:start
[both] So good!

00:51:17.251 --> 00:51:19.521 position:30% line:89% align:start
[both laughing]

00:51:28.329 --> 00:51:30.533 position:19% line:89% align:start
Better when it's messy!

00:51:30.566 --> 00:51:32.568 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:51:32.601 --> 00:51:33.669 position:41% line:89% align:start
This is fun!

00:51:33.702 --> 00:51:36.238 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:51:37.173 --> 00:51:39.108 position:21% line:89% align:start
Hey, how about these?

00:51:39.141 --> 00:51:41.343 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:51:44.046 --> 00:51:46.282 position:30% line:89% align:start
Fun! Better when messy!

00:51:51.321 --> 00:51:53.623 position:38% line:77% align:start
[clattering]
[laughing]

00:52:01.332 --> 00:52:02.667 position:35% line:89% align:start
[both gasp]

00:52:07.171 --> 00:52:09.775 position:24% line:83% align:start
My mom's back.
Oh, no!

00:52:09.808 --> 00:52:11.242 position:24% line:89% align:start
She'll be mad.

00:52:16.147 --> 00:52:17.449 position:30% line:89% align:start
You have to go now!

00:52:18.717 --> 00:52:20.185 position:33% line:89% align:start
[door thuds]

00:52:23.589 --> 00:52:26.024 position:5% line:83% align:start
[grandma]
I don't believe this!

00:52:26.058 --> 00:52:30.062 position:5% line:83% align:start
What is wrong with you?
It's a disaster in here.

00:52:30.430 --> 00:52:32.365 position:19% line:89% align:start
That's it, I've had it!

00:52:32.398 --> 00:52:34.334 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm throwing away
all of your toys!

00:52:34.367 --> 00:52:36.069 position:27% line:89% align:start
Every single one!

00:52:36.102 --> 00:52:38.238 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] Mom, please don't
do that, it won't happen again.

00:52:38.271 --> 00:52:40.574 position:21% line:89% align:start
I promise, I'm sorry!

00:52:40.608 --> 00:52:43.611 position:19% line:77% align:start
[grandma]
And I'm not buying you
any more candy either!

00:52:43.644 --> 00:52:49.049 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] No, please.
I'm sorry, Mom. I'm so sorry!

00:52:49.083 --> 00:52:51.552 position:27% line:89% align:start
[rain whooshing]

00:53:12.441 --> 00:53:13.743 position:55% line:89% align:start
Did he eat?

00:53:13.776 --> 00:53:15.043 position:5% line:89% align:start
He won't wake up.

00:53:15.845 --> 00:53:17.680 position:5% line:89% align:start
My sweet little angel.

00:53:21.384 --> 00:53:24.186 position:27% line:83% align:start
[grandma] I used to call
you that all the time.

00:53:24.220 --> 00:53:26.088 position:5% line:83% align:start
Yeah, where do you think
I got it from?

00:53:26.122 --> 00:53:27.591 position:66% line:89% align:start
[giggling]

00:53:28.992 --> 00:53:32.796 position:13% line:77% align:start
I'm still sore
that you wouldn't let me
adopt one of those strays.

00:53:32.829 --> 00:53:34.765 position:13% line:89% align:start
You were a terror.

00:53:34.798 --> 00:53:38.101 position:21% line:77% align:start
You know, as a kid
I was convinced you
loved me more than Yoichi?

00:53:38.135 --> 00:53:40.471 position:30% line:83% align:start
Now, I know exactly how
a little troublemaker

00:53:40.505 --> 00:53:41.873 position:44% line:83% align:start
can worm their way
into your heart.

00:53:41.906 --> 00:53:44.776 position:5% line:83% align:start
You were definitely
a handful as a child.

00:53:44.809 --> 00:53:47.779 position:5% line:83% align:start
So mischievous
and impossibly stubborn.

00:53:47.812 --> 00:53:51.182 position:5% line:83% align:start
I was constantly losing
my temper with you.

00:53:51.215 --> 00:53:52.317 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh, is that true?

00:53:52.350 --> 00:53:54.419 position:5% line:83% align:start
I could never get you
to tidy up.

00:53:54.452 --> 00:53:57.389 position:41% line:77% align:start
Yeah, I don't think
I actually started
doing any cleaning

00:53:57.423 --> 00:53:58.891 position:21% line:89% align:start
until after I got married.

00:53:58.924 --> 00:54:00.693 position:16% line:89% align:start
Unbelievable.

00:54:03.930 --> 00:54:05.732 position:13% line:89% align:start
I love my job, I really do,

00:54:05.765 --> 00:54:09.536 position:16% line:77% align:start
but I also wanna take
the time to raise my kids
the best way I can.

00:54:10.437 --> 00:54:13.473 position:16% line:83% align:start
So when I lose my temper,
it just kills me.

00:54:13.506 --> 00:54:15.609 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm doing the best I can,
but I'm not sure.

00:54:15.642 --> 00:54:17.410 position:24% line:89% align:start
Am I a good mother?

00:54:19.914 --> 00:54:23.884 position:10% line:83% align:start
In the end, all I really want
is for them to be happy.

00:54:24.485 --> 00:54:27.521 position:16% line:83% align:start
I think you just answered
your own question.

00:54:27.555 --> 00:54:31.125 position:13% line:83% align:start
Raising kids is
all about good intentions.

00:54:33.461 --> 00:54:35.329 position:27% line:89% align:start
Good intentions.

00:54:52.314 --> 00:54:53.650 position:50% line:89% align:start
[Kun] It's okay.

00:55:08.297 --> 00:55:12.770 position:30% line:89% align:start
[horn blaring]

00:55:18.943 --> 00:55:20.912 position:33% line:83% align:start
[father]
What a brilliant idea.

00:55:21.278 --> 00:55:23.615 position:24% line:83% align:start
That letter in Mom's shoe
really worked.

00:55:23.648 --> 00:55:26.284 position:19% line:83% align:start
Where did you even get
an idea like that, huh?

00:55:26.317 --> 00:55:28.787 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey, maybe I should
try that sometime too.

00:55:29.254 --> 00:55:30.221 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gurgling]

00:55:30.255 --> 00:55:31.723 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh, yes, I see you, baby.

00:55:33.025 --> 00:55:37.663 position:19% line:89% align:start
[making animal sounds]

00:55:41.400 --> 00:55:42.668 position:33% line:89% align:start
Not even a smile, huh?

00:56:00.955 --> 00:56:02.957 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:56:02.990 --> 00:56:04.625 position:21% line:89% align:start
[bicycle bell rings]

00:56:04.659 --> 00:56:07.328 position:24% line:83% align:start
Huh? You want me to take
your training wheels off?

00:56:07.361 --> 00:56:08.896 position:44% line:77% align:start
Hmm.
Like right now?

00:56:08.930 --> 00:56:10.031 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:56:10.064 --> 00:56:11.799 position:30% line:83% align:start
You wanna ride
completely on your own?

00:56:11.833 --> 00:56:12.834 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:56:14.002 --> 00:56:15.037 position:58% line:89% align:start
Are you sure?

00:56:15.070 --> 00:56:16.739 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:56:29.551 --> 00:56:31.553 position:30% line:77% align:start
You gonna be all right?
Teach me.

00:56:31.587 --> 00:56:33.623 position:55% line:89% align:start
Oh, right.

00:56:33.656 --> 00:56:35.458 position:44% line:83% align:start
You put your foot
on the pedal

00:56:35.492 --> 00:56:37.594 position:33% line:83% align:start
and then you
push down really hard.

00:56:37.627 --> 00:56:39.829 position:50% line:77% align:start
No, wait!
[crying out]

00:56:40.730 --> 00:56:42.732 position:52% line:77% align:start
[babbles]
He's okay.

00:56:42.766 --> 00:56:44.835 position:16% line:83% align:start
[father] Okay, there you go,
now don't stop.

00:56:44.869 --> 00:56:47.303 position:24% line:83% align:start
That's good, that's good!
You're getting it, yes!

00:56:47.337 --> 00:56:48.739 position:5% line:77% align:start
[thuds]
[crying out]

00:56:48.773 --> 00:56:50.474 position:16% line:83% align:start
You hurt?
You okay?

00:56:50.508 --> 00:56:53.577 position:10% line:89% align:start
No! [crying]

00:56:53.878 --> 00:56:57.581 position:10% line:83% align:start
Right foot, left foot,
keep on going, there you go.

00:56:57.615 --> 00:56:59.017 position:61% line:77% align:start
[thuds]
[crying out]

00:57:01.452 --> 00:57:02.687 position:24% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:57:03.755 --> 00:57:05.524 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell, grunt]

00:57:06.024 --> 00:57:08.326 position:13% line:89% align:start
I can't do it!

00:57:08.360 --> 00:57:10.428 position:50% line:83% align:start
Oh, it's okay,
you'll get it.

00:57:10.462 --> 00:57:12.631 position:21% line:77% align:start
It's too hard.
I know.

00:57:12.932 --> 00:57:14.867 position:5% line:83% align:start
[child] Is this
your first bike?

00:57:14.901 --> 00:57:16.334 position:58% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:57:16.736 --> 00:57:18.004 position:30% line:89% align:start
Are you just learning?

00:57:18.037 --> 00:57:20.506 position:5% line:83% align:start
[child] We can teach you.
It's not that hard.

00:57:20.540 --> 00:57:22.341 position:55% line:77% align:start
[Mirai crying]
Uh...

00:57:23.409 --> 00:57:25.511 position:5% line:83% align:start
Hey, you wanna try practicing
with these boys?

00:57:25.545 --> 00:57:26.612 position:55% line:89% align:start
[Mirai crying]

00:57:26.646 --> 00:57:28.414 position:33% line:89% align:start
Hang on! Coming, baby!

00:57:28.447 --> 00:57:29.515 position:55% line:89% align:start
But, Daddy!

00:57:29.549 --> 00:57:31.985 position:55% line:89% align:start
[Mirai crying]

00:57:33.153 --> 00:57:34.855 position:16% line:89% align:start
She just started crying.

00:57:34.888 --> 00:57:36.990 position:7% line:83% align:start
[father] Oh, thank you,
thank you. Yeah, she's colicky.

00:57:37.024 --> 00:57:39.827 position:27% line:83% align:start
You can think of it
like kicking behind you.

00:57:39.860 --> 00:57:41.695 position:13% line:83% align:start
You just gotta
push down really hard.

00:57:41.728 --> 00:57:43.031 position:38% line:89% align:start
And don't stop.

00:57:43.064 --> 00:57:44.632 position:5% line:77% align:start
Yeah, we'll wait over there.
Come on, let's go!

00:57:44.666 --> 00:57:46.534 position:5% line:83% align:start
[child] Hey, guys,
wait up!

00:57:52.040 --> 00:57:53.942 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm scared, Dad.

00:57:54.876 --> 00:57:55.978 position:41% line:89% align:start
Daddy!

00:57:58.413 --> 00:57:59.582 position:5% line:5% align:start
Is something wrong?

00:57:59.615 --> 00:58:01.483 position:38% line:5% align:start
Yeah, you all right?

00:58:01.517 --> 00:58:03.519 position:35% line:77% align:start
Working from home,
it gives me more time
to be with the kids.

00:58:03.552 --> 00:58:05.421 position:5% line:83% align:start
[child gasps]
I think he's gonna cry.

00:58:05.454 --> 00:58:07.656 position:27% line:83% align:start
[child] Are you serious?
But why?

00:58:08.891 --> 00:58:10.793 position:41% line:89% align:start
Daddy!

00:58:12.062 --> 00:58:14.030 position:27% line:89% align:start
You're so stupid!

00:58:14.965 --> 00:58:17.667 position:27% line:83% align:start
You left me!
I hate you, I hate you!

00:58:17.701 --> 00:58:19.703 position:5% line:83% align:start
[father] Hey!
We'll go again sometime!

00:58:19.736 --> 00:58:21.671 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Kun] I don't wanna
ever go again!

00:58:21.705 --> 00:58:23.473 position:16% line:83% align:start
Don't say that,
you were so close.

00:58:23.506 --> 00:58:24.674 position:5% line:89% align:start
It'll be a breeze next time.

00:58:24.708 --> 00:58:26.811 position:38% line:83% align:start
I don't care!
I don't wanna do it!

00:58:26.844 --> 00:58:29.113 position:83% line:77% align:start
No!
Come here, no, hey!

00:58:31.449 --> 00:58:32.717 position:27% line:89% align:start
[door slams shut]

00:58:35.453 --> 00:58:38.090 position:13% line:89% align:start
[gurgling]

00:58:39.457 --> 00:58:41.159 position:21% line:89% align:start
That's your great-grandpa.

00:58:41.193 --> 00:58:42.593 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Mirai gurgling]

00:58:43.028 --> 00:58:47.032 position:5% line:83% align:start
[straining] I hate it!
Stupid, stupid Daddy!

00:58:48.600 --> 00:58:49.935 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:58:53.605 --> 00:58:57.010 position:33% line:77% align:start
[whooshing]
[crying out]

00:59:10.490 --> 00:59:12.126 position:35% line:89% align:start
[coughing]

00:59:15.496 --> 00:59:16.830 position:33% line:89% align:start
What is that?

00:59:24.739 --> 00:59:26.808 position:27% line:89% align:start
[engine rumbling]

00:59:47.797 --> 00:59:48.965 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:59:52.235 --> 00:59:53.636 position:30% line:89% align:start
Can I help you?

00:59:53.804 --> 00:59:56.206 position:21% line:89% align:start
[nervously grunting]

00:59:58.175 --> 01:00:00.677 position:21% line:83% align:start
Did you wanna know
more about the bike?

01:00:02.213 --> 01:00:04.514 position:24% line:83% align:start
You wanna ride it?
[chuckles]

01:00:04.548 --> 01:00:06.717 position:21% line:83% align:start
It's okay if you do,
no need to be shy.

01:00:07.684 --> 01:00:11.222 position:5% line:83% align:start
Come on, kid, just say the word.
You're really missing out.

01:00:11.689 --> 01:00:14.492 position:41% line:77% align:start
And you won't know
what you're missing
if you don't try.

01:00:14.959 --> 01:00:17.061 position:33% line:89% align:start
Is that true?

01:00:17.262 --> 01:00:18.663 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's right.

01:00:18.696 --> 01:00:20.165 position:13% line:89% align:start
Just like the saying goes.

01:00:20.199 --> 01:00:22.101 position:24% line:89% align:start
[cicadas chirping]

01:00:44.291 --> 01:00:46.926 position:27% line:89% align:start
[gasps] Your leg.

01:00:47.627 --> 01:00:48.695 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

01:00:48.728 --> 01:00:50.097 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Kun] Does it hurt?

01:00:50.131 --> 01:00:52.833 position:24% line:83% align:start
What, this?
It's from the war.

01:00:52.867 --> 01:00:54.301 position:13% line:89% align:start
The ship I was on capsized

01:00:54.335 --> 01:00:57.004 position:10% line:83% align:start
and my leg got injured
when it happened, that's all.

01:00:57.838 --> 01:00:59.874 position:21% line:83% align:start
It's funny,
it used to bother me

01:00:59.907 --> 01:01:02.110 position:24% line:83% align:start
but I hardly even
notice it anymore.

01:01:11.953 --> 01:01:15.557 position:27% line:83% align:start
Hey, it's okay.
You can come in.

01:01:16.392 --> 01:01:17.927 position:27% line:89% align:start
[horses neighing]

01:01:19.896 --> 01:01:21.964 position:24% line:83% align:start
It's just,
it's my first time.

01:01:21.998 --> 01:01:23.966 position:16% line:89% align:start
Uh, your first time what?

01:01:26.769 --> 01:01:28.004 position:5% line:89% align:start
The horse?

01:01:28.771 --> 01:01:30.240 position:5% line:89% align:start
Your first?

01:01:30.274 --> 01:01:31.908 position:13% line:89% align:start
Your very first?

01:01:36.213 --> 01:01:37.614 position:21% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

01:01:37.648 --> 01:01:38.816 position:5% line:89% align:start
Anyone here?

01:01:38.849 --> 01:01:39.917 position:41% line:89% align:start
We are.

01:01:39.950 --> 01:01:41.352 position:5% line:83% align:start
[man] Can you
tack up my horse?

01:01:41.386 --> 01:01:43.987 position:24% line:77% align:start
