01:01:51.229 --> 01:01:52.263 position:35% line:89% align:start
Here we go!

01:01:53.364 --> 01:01:54.799 position:38% line:89% align:start
So cool!

01:01:54.833 --> 01:01:56.201 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

01:01:57.769 --> 01:01:58.770 position:41% line:89% align:start
Ready?

01:01:58.803 --> 01:02:00.905 position:16% line:89% align:start
