01:03:05.508 --> 01:03:07.411 position:44% line:77% align:start
Hmm.
[chuckles]

01:03:08.912 --> 01:03:10.314 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:03:21.292 --> 01:03:23.160 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

01:03:23.761 --> 01:03:25.029 position:19% line:89% align:start
