01:03:27.898 --> 01:03:31.069 position:7% line:89% align:start
Good. Now I'm gonna go faster.

01:03:31.102 --> 01:03:33.972 position:24% line:89% align:start
[hooves clattering]

01:03:39.044 --> 01:03:41.447 position:27% line:89% align:start
[engine rumbling]

01:03:56.796 --> 01:03:58.198 position:19% line:89% align:start
