you can ride anything at all.

01:05:02.467 --> 01:05:08.005 position:7% line:83% align:start
It could be a horse,
or a ship, or even an airplane.

01:05:14.579 --> 01:05:15.981 position:41% line:89% align:start
Daddy?

01:05:16.014 --> 01:05:17.115 position:33% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

01:05:17.617 --> 01:05:18.850 position:33% line:89% align:start
This is cool.

