01:05:27.527 --> 01:05:28.561 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

01:05:55.090 --> 01:05:56.324 position:33% line:89% align:start
[father] I'm so sorry.

01:05:56.358 --> 01:05:58.293 position:5% line:83% align:start
