01:06:01.630 --> 01:06:04.233 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] You specifically
told me you'd send it.

01:06:05.100 --> 01:06:08.170 position:21% line:83% align:start
I can't go back in time,
what do you want me to do?

01:06:08.604 --> 01:06:10.339 position:44% line:77% align:start
Dad?
Hmm?

01:06:10.539 --> 01:06:12.041 position:33% line:89% align:start
Good morning.

01:06:12.074 --> 01:06:14.110 position:5% line:89% align:start
[father] Good morning to you.

01:06:14.143 --> 01:06:15.378 position:21% line:89% align:start
Take me to the park.

01:06:15.411 --> 01:06:16.912 position:5% line:89% align:start
