01:06:16.946 --> 01:06:18.648 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'm going to ride my bike.

01:06:18.682 --> 01:06:20.550 position:10% line:77% align:start
[father] What?
Come on!

01:06:22.986 --> 01:06:25.322 position:13% line:83% align:start
Hey, you sure you don't
need me out there with you?

01:06:25.355 --> 01:06:26.890 position:33% line:89% align:start
I'll be fine.

01:06:39.637 --> 01:06:40.571 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

01:06:40.972 --> 01:06:42.106 position:35% line:89% align:start
[exclaims]

01:06:53.152 --> 01:06:54.052 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

01:06:54.888 --> 01:06:57.122 position:24% line:83% align:start
You're doing great,
don't give up!

01:06:58.725 --> 01:07:01.193 position:21% line:89% align:start
Don't give up. Okay.

01:07:03.128 --> 01:07:05.398 position:35% line:89% align:start
[straining]

01:07:05.732 --> 01:07:06.699 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thuds]

01:07:06.733 --> 01:07:08.034 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ah...

01:07:08.067 --> 01:07:10.170 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

01:07:15.208 --> 01:07:17.411 position:19% line:89% align:start
Look into the distance.

01:07:19.713 --> 01:07:22.316 position:21% line:89% align:start
[soft music playing]

01:07:26.688 --> 01:07:29.691 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh, yes, you got it!

01:07:30.692 --> 01:07:32.494 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

01:07:38.400 --> 01:07:40.603 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh, yeah! Yes, yes!

01:07:53.082 --> 01:07:54.350 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes!

01:07:54.383 --> 01:07:57.286 position:27% line:83% align:start
You're doing it!
Go, Kun, go!

01:07:57.320 --> 01:07:58.722 position:38% line:89% align:start
[cheers]

01:08:03.327 --> 01:08:05.095 position:50% line:83% align:start
Once you get it,
it's real easy.

01:08:05.128 --> 01:08:06.196 position:5% line:83% align:start
It's a piece of cake,
right?

01:08:06.230 --> 01:08:07.264 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ride with us!

01:08:07.297 --> 01:08:08.398 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yeah, it'll be fun!

01:08:08.432 --> 01:08:11.034 position:66% line:77% align:start
Yeah!
All right. Follow me.

01:08:11.068 --> 01:08:12.570 position:5% line:89% align:start
Come on, let's go.

01:08:18.743 --> 01:08:21.045 position:5% line:89% align:start
Hey! Wait up!

01:08:21.079 --> 01:08:23.314 position:5% line:89% align:start
I am so proud of you!

01:08:23.348 --> 01:08:25.718 position:13% line:83% align:start
Good job, Kun!
You know what?

01:08:25.751 --> 01:08:29.355 position:5% line:77% align:start
I bet you it really helped
that his dad was there
to cheer him on.

01:08:29.388 --> 01:08:31.123 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yeah, you think so?

01:08:31.156 --> 01:08:32.525 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Yumi] Oh, I know so.

01:08:42.769 --> 01:08:44.771 position:27% line:83% align:start
Children are incredible,
aren't they?

01:08:45.572 --> 01:08:47.741 position:27% line:83% align:start
