taught him how to do it.

01:08:47.774 --> 01:08:50.510 position:13% line:83% align:start
He kept on falling,
but he just wouldn't give up.

01:08:50.544 --> 01:08:52.747 position:5% line:83% align:start
You know what else?
Have you noticed?

01:08:52.780 --> 01:08:55.348 position:5% line:83% align:start
Mirai doesn't cry anymore
when you hold her.

01:08:55.382 --> 01:08:56.450 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah?

01:08:56.484 --> 01:08:58.386 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Yumi] And she looks calm.

01:08:58.419 --> 01:09:01.088 position:5% line:77% align:start
You never gave up
and you learned how
to hold her.

01:09:01.122 --> 01:09:05.761 position:16% line:77% align:start
No, no, no, come on
this really shouldn't be
about me, this is about Kun.

01:09:05.794 --> 01:09:07.295 position:58% line:89% align:start
It's his day.

01:09:08.262 --> 01:09:09.598 position:19% line:89% align:start
As you wish.

01:09:09.865 --> 01:09:11.466 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Kun gasps] This is Dad!

01:09:11.500 --> 01:09:13.335 position:13% line:77% align:start
Huh, which one?
[Kun] This one.

01:09:13.368 --> 01:09:15.504 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Yumi laughs]
No, that's not your dad,

01:09:15.537 --> 01:09:17.372 position:5% line:89% align:start
that's your great-grandpa.

01:09:18.407 --> 01:09:20.208 position:27% line:89% align:start
Mm-mm. It's Dad.

01:09:20.242 --> 01:09:24.079 position:5% line:77% align:start
[Yumi]
No, it is your great-grandpa.
He died last year.

01:09:25.147 --> 01:09:26.416 position:30% line:89% align:start
Great-Grandpa?

01:09:26.449 --> 01:09:27.650 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Yumi] That's right.

01:09:27.684 --> 01:09:30.453 position:5% line:83% align:start
He built engines
for fighter planes.

01:09:30.486 --> 01:09:33.489 position:5% line:83% align:start
Then later during the war
he was drafted,

01:09:33.523 --> 01:09:36.159 position:5% line:83% align:start
and the ship that he was on
was attacked.

01:09:36.392 --> 01:09:38.596 position:5% line:83% align:start
He got badly injured
but he survived.

01:09:39.295 --> 01:09:43.400 position:5% line:83% align:start
Then, after the war, he got
a job at a motorcycle company.

01:09:47.738 --> 01:09:50.809 position:21% line:83% align:start
Oh, I see,
so that's who he was.

01:09:53.177 --> 01:09:54.879 position:16% line:89% align:start
Thank you, Great-Grandpa.

01:10:01.453 --> 01:10:02.888 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Kun] No!

01:10:02.922 --> 01:10:04.556 position:7% line:83% align:start
[father] Uh, yeah, those look,
those are terrible.

01:10:04.589 --> 01:10:06.559 position:19% line:89% align:start
Oh, how about this one?

01:10:06.592 --> 01:10:08.794 position:30% line:83% align:start
No!
Where's the yellow one?

01:10:08.828 --> 01:10:09.929 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's in the laundry.

01:10:09.962 --> 01:10:11.597 position:21% line:89% align:start
But I want the yellow one.

01:10:11.631 --> 01:10:14.400 position:5% line:77% align:start
You can't, it's not dry yet.
I don't care!

01:10:14.433 --> 01:10:16.202 position:5% line:83% align:start
Then do you wanna go
without any pants?

01:10:16.235 --> 01:10:17.503 position:52% line:89% align:start
No, I don't!

01:10:17.536 --> 01:10:19.238 position:5% line:83% align:start
Well, you're gonna have
to wear this one then.

01:10:19.271 --> 01:10:20.473 position:5% line:89% align:start
This is giving me a headache.

01:10:20.506 --> 01:10:21.675 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Yukko barks]

01:10:21.708 --> 01:10:23.910 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] Whatcha doing there?
Come here.

01:10:25.712 --> 01:10:28.448 position:33% line:83% align:start
Sit tight,
let's get you dressed.

01:10:28.482 --> 01:10:30.283 position:16% line:83% align:start
Mom, I wanna wear
my yellow pants.

01:10:30.317 --> 01:10:32.920 position:16% line:83% align:start
Yukko, please stop barking.
You're giving me a headache.

01:10:32.954 --> 01:10:34.321 position:24% line:89% align:start
I don't like these pants!

01:10:34.354 --> 01:10:35.255 position:35% line:89% align:start
Those look fine.

01:10:35.957 --> 01:10:37.725 position:5% line:77% align:start
