everything around here?

01:10:46.300 --> 01:10:48.737 position:5% line:83% align:start
Coming through.
I got it!

01:10:48.771 --> 01:10:51.607 position:5% line:89% align:start
I hate these pants forever!

01:10:51.640 --> 01:10:53.409 position:5% line:89% align:start
I want the yellow ones!

01:10:53.442 --> 01:10:54.610 position:35% line:83% align:start
What do you think
you're doing?

01:10:54.643 --> 01:10:56.211 position:5% line:83% align:start
[father] Honey,
do you have the keys?

01:10:56.245 --> 01:10:58.347 position:30% line:83% align:start
Yes, just hang on.
I'm coming down now.

01:10:58.380 --> 01:10:59.782 position:5% line:89% align:start
We'll be there in a sec.

01:11:03.318 --> 01:11:04.888 position:19% line:89% align:start
