01:11:04.921 --> 01:11:07.590 position:19% line:83% align:start
they love Mirai
more than they love me.

01:11:09.259 --> 01:11:11.628 position:38% line:71% align:start
[cries out]
[Yumi] Hurry up, Kun,
we gotta go.

01:11:11.661 --> 01:11:14.364 position:35% line:71% align:start
I'm not going!
[Yumi] What are you
going to do then?

01:11:14.397 --> 01:11:15.833 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm running away!

01:11:15.866 --> 01:11:17.500 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] Oh, you mean
to your room?

01:11:17.534 --> 01:11:20.538 position:27% line:83% align:start
Yeah, and I'm not
coming back!

01:11:21.271 --> 01:11:22.773 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh, Kun.

01:11:25.009 --> 01:11:25.943 position:5% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

01:11:26.944 --> 01:11:27.912 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

01:11:30.816 --> 01:11:33.451 position:13% line:89% align:start
