01:11:36.888 --> 01:11:37.889 position:61% line:89% align:start
[yells]

01:11:40.692 --> 01:11:42.761 position:35% line:89% align:start
Goodbye, forever!

01:11:45.898 --> 01:11:46.933 position:47% line:89% align:start
[groans]

01:11:46.966 --> 01:11:49.434 position:30% line:83% align:start
Why aren't you
looking for me?

01:11:53.005 --> 01:11:54.474 position:55% line:89% align:start
Hello?

01:11:55.608 --> 01:11:57.010 position:27% line:89% align:start
Where did you go?

01:11:58.478 --> 01:12:00.546 position:16% line:89% align:start
Did you leave without me?

01:12:01.982 --> 01:12:04.250 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]

01:12:04.885 --> 01:12:07.454 position:27% line:83% align:start
I don't care,
I don't like you!

01:12:12.426 --> 01:12:14.796 position:33% line:89% align:start
[sobbing]

01:12:17.364 --> 01:12:18.933 position:27% line:89% align:start
[man] That's just awful.

01:12:22.737 --> 01:12:24.739 position:10% line:89% align:start
[man 2] Yup, a complete wreck.

01:12:24.773 --> 01:12:26.976 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm talking about
your attitude.

01:12:27.009 --> 01:12:28.710 position:24% line:89% align:start
Boy, does it stink.

01:12:33.082 --> 01:12:34.583 position:33% line:89% align:start
Hello?

01:12:34.617 --> 01:12:36.318 position:30% line:83% align:start
You're supposed to
go camping, am I right?

01:12:36.352 --> 01:12:38.988 position:16% line:83% align:start
Catch bugs, watch fireworks,
all that stuff.

01:12:39.021 --> 01:12:41.992 position:16% line:83% align:start
