you're sorry already.

01:13:03.514 --> 01:13:04.649 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Kun] No.

01:13:05.750 --> 01:13:07.518 position:24% line:89% align:start
I do not like them.

01:13:07.552 --> 01:13:08.619 position:52% line:89% align:start
[boy] What?

01:13:08.653 --> 01:13:10.521 position:5% line:89% align:start
And I will not wear them!

01:13:10.856 --> 01:13:12.858 position:35% line:83% align:start
No, you do not
not like them.

01:13:12.891 --> 01:13:14.860 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Kun] No, I don't not
not like them!

01:13:14.893 --> 01:13:17.529 position:24% line:83% align:start
[boy] No, you do not
not, not, not, like them!

01:13:17.563 --> 01:13:19.031 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Kun] Yes I do not
not, not, not like them!

01:13:19.064 --> 01:13:22.668 position:27% line:83% align:start
No, you do not not, not,
not, not, not like them!

01:13:27.539 --> 01:13:28.942 position:33% line:89% align:start
Don't get on!

01:13:29.642 --> 01:13:31.744 position:16% line:89% align:start
Stop! Don't get on, 'kay?

01:13:33.179 --> 01:13:35.014 position:30% line:89% align:start
[whistle blows]

01:13:35.782 --> 01:13:37.650 position:21% line:89% align:start
[boy] No! Wait, wait!

01:13:38.418 --> 01:13:40.921 position:27% line:89% align:start
[engine rumbling]

01:13:47.428 --> 01:13:48.696 position:33% line:89% align:start
Little brat.

01:13:55.569 --> 01:13:56.705 position:50% line:89% align:start
Tanker train!

01:13:59.074 --> 01:14:00.575 position:50% line:89% align:start
A freight train!

01:14:00.809 --> 01:14:02.711 position:19% line:89% align:start
It's a Narita Express!

01:14:02.744 --> 01:14:04.746 position:21% line:89% align:start
The Ueno-Tokyo line!

