01:27:59.739 --> 01:28:01.007 position:35% line:89% align:start
You're really fast.

01:28:05.678 --> 01:28:07.914 position:21% line:89% align:start
[laughs] Silly.

01:28:08.782 --> 01:28:10.050 position:24% line:89% align:start
Back when he was injured,

01:28:10.084 --> 01:28:13.486 position:16% line:83% align:start
if Great-Grandpa didn't swim
as hard as he could,

01:28:13.520 --> 01:28:14.822 position:33% line:89% align:start
and then Great-Granny,

01:28:14.855 --> 01:28:17.725 position:16% line:83% align:start
if she didn't decide
to lose the race on purpose,

01:28:17.758 --> 01:28:19.794 position:41% line:83% align:start
none of us would be
here right now.

01:28:21.362 --> 01:28:23.731 position:41% line:83% align:start
These little things
all come together

01:28:23.764 --> 01:28:25.766 position:47% line:83% align:start
to make up
who we are today.

01:28:26.567 --> 01:28:30.071 position:21% line:83% align:start
Everyone in our family is
a result of these moments.

01:28:31.372 --> 01:28:32.774 position:35% line:89% align:start
We are?

01:28:33.909 --> 01:28:36.812 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whooshes]

01:29:02.573 --> 01:29:03.941 position:5% line:89% align:start
Hey, Kun.

01:29:05.542 --> 01:29:07.946 position:5% line:83% align:start
I think Mom and Dad
are looking for you.

01:29:09.446 --> 01:29:10.915 position:55% line:89% align:start
Don't do that.

01:29:10.949 --> 01:29:11.983 position:5% line:89% align:start
Do what?

01:29:12.016 --> 01:29:15.453 position:10% line:83% align:start
Don't be barbaric,
sit down at the dining table.

01:29:15.486 --> 01:29:16.554 position:10% line:89% align:start
Do you want some?

01:29:16.588 --> 01:29:17.922 position:5% line:89% align:start
No, thanks.

01:29:23.561 --> 01:29:26.165 position:19% line:89% align:start
Mirai from the future?

01:29:26.198 --> 01:29:29.134 position:13% line:83% align:start
Mm-mmm. Actually,
this is me in the present.

01:29:29.168 --> 01:29:31.971 position:16% line:83% align:start
You're the one who's
from the past right now.

01:29:32.004 --> 01:29:33.706 position:27% line:89% align:start
In other words...

01:29:34.907 --> 01:29:37.610 position:19% line:83% align:start
That guy just now,
do you know who he is?

01:29:37.643 --> 01:29:38.945 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mm-hmm.

01:29:39.746 --> 01:29:41.615 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Mirai] Pretty cool, huh?

01:29:42.514 --> 01:29:44.684 position:27% line:83% align:start
It's time for you
to go home

01:29:44.718 --> 01:29:46.953 position:24% line:83% align:start
and try not
to get lost, okay?

01:29:47.520 --> 01:29:48.788 position:27% line:89% align:start
Is this goodbye?

01:29:48.822 --> 01:29:50.724 position:30% line:89% align:start
Don't be silly.

01:29:50.757 --> 01:29:54.028 position:13% line:77% align:start
Now you had better
get going before you start
getting sick of me.

01:29:54.061 --> 01:29:56.030 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whooshes]

01:30:37.507 --> 01:30:39.743 position:10% line:83% align:start
[father] How's your headache,
is it gone?

01:30:39.777 --> 01:30:41.145 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Yumi] Finally, thank God.

01:30:41.178 --> 01:30:43.647 position:19% line:83% align:start
[father] You gotta
take care of yourself, too.

01:30:45.516 --> 01:30:48.018 position:33% line:83% align:start
I appreciate how sweet
you've been lately.

01:30:48.053 --> 01:30:49.154 position:16% line:89% align:start
Who, me?

01:30:49.187 --> 01:30:51.522 position:30% line:83% align:start
You never were
this thoughtful before.

01:30:51.555 --> 01:30:52.589 position:19% line:89% align:start
Like when?

01:30:52.623 --> 01:30:55.026 position:27% line:89% align:start
Like, when Kun was born.

01:30:55.060 --> 01:30:56.061 position:16% line:89% align:start
[father] Yeah.

01:30:56.094 --> 01:30:58.263 position:30% line:83% align:start
Working and being a dad
was too much for you.

01:30:58.296 --> 01:30:59.931 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh, and it wasn't for you?

01:30:59.965 --> 01:31:02.567 position:19% line:89% align:start
Me? I'm the same as always.

01:31:02.600 --> 01:31:03.935 position:5% line:89% align:start
You're unflappable now.

01:31:03.970 --> 01:31:05.071 position:50% line:89% align:start
Huh?

01:31:05.104 --> 01:31:09.141 position:5% line:83% align:start
I get it, it was tough,
but you were just always angry.

01:31:09.175 --> 01:31:12.979 position:10% line:83% align:start
[sighs] You're right,
I'd blocked it out of my mind.

01:31:13.012 --> 01:31:16.048 position:5% line:83% align:start
But I think we did
a decent job, didn't we?

01:31:16.082 --> 01:31:19.119 position:24% line:83% align:start
Truth is we really owe it
to our kids.

01:31:25.058 --> 01:31:28.061 position:5% line:83% align:start
[father] So, do you think
I'm a good dad now?

01:31:28.695 --> 01:31:30.931 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Yumi] I'd say you're okay.

01:31:30.964 --> 01:31:32.200 position:5% line:89% align:start
[father] Just okay?

01:31:32.233 --> 01:31:33.935 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] What about me,
am I a good mom?

01:31:33.968 --> 01:31:36.270 position:5% line:83% align:start
Really good.
Not perfect, but who is?

01:31:36.304 --> 01:31:38.006 position:41% line:83% align:start
You know what,
I'm okay with that,

01:31:38.039 --> 01:31:40.041 position:44% line:83% align:start
as long as I'm not
a bad mom.

01:31:40.842 --> 01:31:42.844 position:55% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

01:31:42.877 --> 01:31:46.115 position:5% line:89% align:start
[both laughing]

01:31:49.784 --> 01:31:51.987 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Yukko] And I'm a good dog.

01:31:56.091 --> 01:31:57.726 position:16% line:89% align:start
[babbles]

01:32:06.236 --> 01:32:07.871 position:41% line:89% align:start
You want some?

01:32:11.741 --> 01:32:13.043 position:44% line:89% align:start
Here you go.

01:32:26.123 --> 01:32:29.727 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] Mirai, Kun, sweetie.
Come on, we're ready!

01:32:29.760 --> 01:32:31.695 position:5% line:77% align:start
[father] Time to hit the road!
Okay!

01:32:31.729 --> 01:32:33.198 position:47% line:89% align:start
[Mirai cries out]

01:32:34.632 --> 01:32:35.634 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

01:32:35.867 --> 01:32:37.869 position:58% line:89% align:start
[screams]

01:32:55.422 --> 01:32:58.258 position:38% line:89% align:start
[screams]

01:33:02.830 --> 01:33:05.165 position:38% line:89% align:start
[screams]

01:33:08.135 --> 01:33:11.839 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Yumi] Come on, family.
Let's get this vacation started!

01:33:13.874 --> 01:33:16.344 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yeah!

01:33:21.950 --> 01:33:23.952 position:30% line:89% align:start
[whistle blows]

01:33:23.985 --> 01:33:26.788 position:30% line:89% align:start
[music playing]

01:33:26.821 --> 01:33:30.825 position:21% line:5% align:start
[singing in Japanese]

01:38:23.071 --> 01:38:25.207 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music fades out]

